hadiths[260]{hadithnumber,text}:
1513,Fazal-bin-Abbaas (hijjatul-wadaa mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sawari ke peechhey baithey huey they ke qabila Khasam ki aik khoobsurat aurat aai. Fazal usko dekhney lagey wo bhi unhein dekh rahi thi. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ka chehra baar-baar dusri taraf mod dena chahtey they. us aurat ne kaha ya Rasulullah! Allah ka fareezae-haj mere walid ke liye ada karna zaroori ho gaya hai. lekin wo bahut boodhey hain ontni par baith nahi saktey. kya main unki taraf se Haj ( badal ( kar sakti hoon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan. ye Hijjatul-wada ka waqia tha.
1514,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zul-Hulaifa mein dekha ke apni sawari par chadh rahe hain. phir jab wo seedhi khadi hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne labbaik kahaa.
1515,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zul-hulaifa se ehram baandha jab sawari Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko lekar seedhi khadi ho gaee. Ibraaheem-bin-Moosaa ki ye hadis Ibne-Abbas aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi marwi (bayan) hai.
1516,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke sath unke bhai Abdur-Rehman ko bheja aur unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko taneem se Umra karaya aur paalaan ki pichhli lakdi par unko bitha liya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Haj ke liye paalaanein baandho kyonke ye bhi aik jihad hai.
1517,"Anas (Raziallahu anhu) aik paalaan par Haj ke liye tashrif le gaey aur aap kanjoos nahi they. aap ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi paalaan par Haj ke liye tashrif le gaey they, usi par aap ka saman bhi lada hua tha."
1518,unhon-ne kaha ya Rasulullah! aap logon ne to Umra kar liya lekin main na kar sakii. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Abdur-Rehman apni behan ko ley ja aur unhein taneem se Umra kara laa. chunanche unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko apne oont ke peechhey bitha liya aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Umra ada kya.
1519,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kisi ne puchha ke kon sa kaam behtar hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah aur uske rasool par eman lana . puchha gaya ke phir iske ba'd? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ke rastey mein jihad karna. phir puchha gaya ke phir iske baad ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haje-mabroor.
1520,unhon-ne puchha ya Rasulullah ! ham dekhtey hain ke jihad sab nek kaamon se badh kar hai. phir ham bhi kyon na jihad karein? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi balke sabse afzal jihad Haj hai jo mabroor ho.
1521,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jis shakhs ne Allah ke liye us shaan ke sath Haj kya ke na koi fuhush baat hui aur na koi gunah to wo us din ki tarah wapas hoga jaisey uski maan ne usey janaa tha.
1522,"wo Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki qiyam gaah par hazir huey. wahan qanaat ke sath shaamiyaana laga hua tha (Zaid-bin-Jubair ne kaha ke) maine puchha ke kis jagah se Umre ka ehram baandhna chahiye Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najad walon ke liye qarn, Madina walon ke liye zul-Hulaifa aur Sham (Syria) walon ke liye Johfa muqarrar kya hai."
1523,Yaman ke log raaste ka kharch sath laey baghair Haj ke liye aa jatey they. kehtey to ye they ke ham twakkul kartey hain lekin jab Makka aatey to logon se maangney lagtey . is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai ''aur khane-pine ka saman ley liya karo ke sabse behtar khane-pine ka saman to taqwa hi hai.'' usko ibne-Uena ne Amr se b-waaste Ikrima mursalan (wo hadis jismein tabaii se uper kisi raawi ka naam n milta ho) naql kya hai.
1524,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina walon ke ehram ke liye zul-Hulaifa, Sham (Syria) walon ke liye Johfa, Najad walon ke qarnulmaanzil, Yaman walon ke Yalamlam mutaiyan kya. yahan se un maqamat waley bhi ehram baandhein aur unke ilawa wo log bhi jawan raston se aaein aur Haj ya Umre ka irada rakhtey hun. lekin jinka qiyam meeqaat aur Makka ke darmyan hai to wo ehram usi jagah se baandhein jahan se unhein safar shuru karna hai. yahan tak ke Makka ke log Makka hi se ehram baandhein."
1525,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Madina ke log zul-Hulaifa se ehram baandhein , Sham (Syria) ke log Johfa se aur Najad ke log Qarnul-Manaazil se. Abdullah ne kaha ke mujhey malum hua hai. ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur Yaman ke log Yalamlam se ehram baandhein ."
1526,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina walon ke liye zul-Hulaifa ko meeqaat muqarrar kya, Sham (Syria) walon ke liye Johfa , Najad walon ke liye Qarnul-Manaazil aur Yaman walon ke liye Yalamlam . ye meeqaat un mulk walon ke hain aur un logon ke liye bhi jawan mulkon se guzar kar haram mein dakhil hon aur Haj ya Umre ka irada rakhtey hun. lekin jo log meeqaat ke andar rahtey hun. yahan tak ke Makka ke log ehram Makka hi se baandhein."
1527,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meeqaat mutaiyan kar diye they.
1528,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke Madina walon ke liye ehram baandhney ki jagah zul-Hulaifa aur Sham (Syria) walon ke liye Mahya yani Johfa aur Najad walon ke liye Qarnul-Manaazil . Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke log kehtey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Yaman waley ehram Yalamlam se baandhein lekin maine usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nahi suna."
1529,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina walon ke liye zul-Hulaifa meeqaat thehraya aur Sham (Syria) walon ke liye Johfa, Yaman walon ke liye Yalamlam aur Najad walon ke liye Qarnul-Manaazil. ye un mulkon ke logon ke liye hain aur doosrey un tamam logon ke liye bhi jawan mulkon se guzrein aur Haj aur Umre ka irada rakhtey hun. lekin jo log meeqaat ke andar rahtey hun. to wo apne shehron se ehram baandhein, yahan tak ke Makka ke log Makka hi se ehram baandhein."
1530,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina walon ke liye zul-Hulaifa ko meeqaat muqarrar kya, Sham (Syria) walon ke liye Johfa , Najad walon ke liye Qarnul-Manaazil aur Yaman walon ke liye Yalamlam. ye un mulkon ke baashindon ke meeqaat hain aur tamam un doosrey musalmanon ke bhi jawan mulkon se guzar kar aaein aur Haj aur Umre ka irada rakhtey hun. lekin jo log meeqaat ke andar rahtey hain to (wo ehram wahin se baandhein) jahan se safar shuru karein yahan tak ke Makka ke log ehram Makka hi se baandhein."
1531,"jab ye 2 Shahar ( Basra aur Kufa ( fateh huey to log umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha ke ya ameerul-momineen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najad ke logon ke liye ehram baandhney ki jagah Qarnul-Manaazil qarar di hai aur hamara rasta idhar se nahi hai, agar ham Qarn ki taraf jayen to hamarey liye badi dushwari hogi. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke phir tum log apne rastey mein iske barabar koi jagah tajwiz kar lo. chunanche unke liye zaate-arq ki ki jagah tay kar di."
1532,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maqam zul-Hulaifa ke pathreeley maidan main apni sawari roki aur phir wahin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aisa hi kya kartey they.
1533,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) shajra ke rastey se guzartey huey ''Maris'' ke rastey se Madina aatey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Makka jatey to shajra ki masjid mein Namaz padhtey lekin waapsii mein zul-Hulaifa ke nasheb (dhaal waley ilaaqe) mein Namaz padhtey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat wahin guzaarey yahan tak ke subah ho jati.
1534,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se wadi aqeeq mein suna. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke raat mere paas mere rab ka aik farishta aaya aur kaha ke us ''mubaarak waadii'' mein Namaz padh aur elaan karke Umra Haj mein Sharik ho gaya.
1535,ma'ris ke qareeb zul-Hulaifa ki batan wadi (waadii aqeeq) mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khuwab dikhaya gaya. (jis mein) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha gaya tha ke aap us waqt ''Bat'haa mubaarka'' mein hain. Musa-bin-Aqba ne kaha ke Salim ne ham ko bhi wahan thehraya wo us maqam ko dhoond rahe they jahan Abdullah oont bithaya kartey they yani jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko utra kartey they. wo maqam us masjid ke nichey ki taraf mein hai jo naley ke nasheb mein hai. utarney walon aur rastey ke beechon-beech (waadii aqeeq Madina se char mail Baqee ki taraf hai).
1536,kabhi aap mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us haal mein dikhaiye jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil ho rahi ho. unhon-ne bayan kya ke aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jaarana main apne sathiyon ki aik jamat ke sath thahrey huey they ke aik shakhs ne aa kar puchha ya Rasulullah ! us shakhs ke mutaalliq aap ka kya hukm hai jisne Umre ka ehram is tarah baandha ke uske kapdey khushbu mein basey huey hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par thodi der ke liye chup ho gaey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil hui to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Yala (Raziallahu anhu) ko ishara kya. Yala aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par aik kapda tha jiske andar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif rakhtey they. unhon-ne kapdey ke andar apna sar kya to kya dekhtey hain ke chehra surkh hai aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kharraatey ley rahe hain. phir ye haalat khatm hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo shakhs kahan hai jisne Umra ke mutaalliq puchha tha. wo shakhs hazir kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo khushbu laga rakhi hai usey teen martaba dho ley aur apna jubba utaar de. Umra mein bhi isi tarah kar jis tarah Haj mein kartey ho. maine Ata se puchha ke kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke teen martaba dhoney ke hukm se poori tarah safaaii murad thi? to unhon-ne kaha ke haan.
1537,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) saada tel istemal kartey they (ehraam ke baawajood) maine iska zikr Ibrahim Nakhai se kya to unhon-ne farmaya ke tum ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat naql kartey ho.
1538,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) hain aur maano mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maang mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun.
1539,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ehram baandhtey to main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ehram ke liye aur isi tarah Baitullah ke tawaafe-ziyarat se pahley halal honey ke liye, khushbu lagaya karti thin."
1540,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Talbeed (baalon ko jamaane) ki haalat mein labbaik kehtey suna.
1541,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid zul-Hulaifa ke qareeb hi pahunch kar ehram baandha tha.
1542,"aik shakhs ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! mohrim ko kis tarah ka kapda pahannaa chaahiye? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya na kurta pahney, na amama baandhey, na paa-jaama pahney, na barsaati koot, na mozey. lekin agar uske paas jootii na ho to wo mozey us waqt pahan sakta hai jab takhnon ke nichey se unko kaat liya ho. (aur ehram mein) koi aisa kapda na pahno jis mein zafran ya waras laga hua ho. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke mohrim apna sar dho sakta hai lekin kangha na kare. badan bhi na khujlaanaa chahiye aur joon sar aur badan se nikal kar zameen par dali ja sakti hai."
1543,"Arafaat se Muzdalfa tak Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari par peechhey baithey huey they. phir Muzdalfa se Mina tak Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) peechhey baith gaey they, donon hazraat ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jamarae-aqba ki rami tak barabar talbiya kehtey rahe."
1544,"Arafaat se Muzdalfa tak Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari par peechhey baithey huey they. phir Muzdalfa se Mina tak Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) peechhey baith gaey they, donon hazraat ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jamara Aqba ki rami tak barabar talbiya kehtey rahe."
1545,"Hijjatul-wada mein Zohar aur Asr ke darmyan hafte ke din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kangha karne aur tel lagaaney aur izaar aur chadar pahnney ke baad apne sahaba ke sath Madina se nikley. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt zafran mein rangey huey aisey kapdey ke siwa jiska rang badan par lagta ho kisi qism ki chadar ya tehband pahnney se mana nahi kya. din mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zul-Hulaifa pahunch gaey (aur raat wahin guzari ( phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sawar huey aur beda se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon ne labbaik kaha aur ehram baandha aur apne oonton ko haar pahnaayaa . Zi-Qada ke mahiney mein ab panch din reh gaey they phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka pahunchey to Zil-Hijja ke char din guzar chukey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ka tawaaf kya aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi halal nahi huey kyonke qurbani ke janwar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki gardan mein haar daal diya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hajoon pahaad ke nazdeek Makka ke oopri hisse mein utrey. Haj ka ehram ab bhi baqi tha. Baitullah ke tawaaf ke baad phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan us waqt tak tashrif nahi le gaey jab tak maidan Arafaat se wapas na ho liye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sathiyon ko hukm diya tha ke wo Baitullah ka tawaaf karein aur Safa w Marwa ke darmyan saee karein, phir apne saron ke baal tarashwa kar halal ho jaaein. ye farman un logon ke liye tha jinke sath qurbani ke janwar nahi they. agar kisi ke sath uski biwi thi to wo us se ham-bistar ho sakta tha. isi tarah khushbu daar aur (siley huey) kapdey ka istemal bhi uske liye jaaiz tha."
1546,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina mein char rakatein padhein lekin zul-Hulaifa mein 2 rakaat ada farmain phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne raat wahin guzari. subah ke waqt jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par Sawar huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne labbaik pukaarii.
1547,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina mein Zohar char rakaat padhi lekin zul-Hulaifa mein Asr 2 rak'at. unhon-ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ke raat subah tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zul-Hulaifa mein hi guzaar di.
1548,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne namaaze-Zuhar Madina Munawra mein char rakaat padhi. lekin namaze-Asr zul-Hulaifa mein 2 rakaat padhi. maine khud suna ke log buland awaz se Haj aur Umra donon ke liye labbaik keh rahe they.
1549,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka talbiya ye thaa  لبيك اللهم لبيك ، Mina لبيك لا شريك لك لبيك ، Mina إن الحمد والنعمة لك والملك ، Mina لا شريك لك''haazir hun aey Allah ! hazir hun mein, tera koi Sharik nahi. hazir hun, tamam hamd terey hi liye hai aur tamam ne'matein teri hi taraf se hain, badhshahat teri hi hai tera koi Sharik nahi.''"
1550,"main janti hun ke kis taraf Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) talbiya kehtey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) talbiya yun kehtey they  لبيك اللهم لبيك ، Mina لبيك لا شريك لك لبيك ، Mina إن الحمد والنعمة لك‏(tarjama guzar chuka hai) uski mutabiat (pairavi) Sufiyan Sory ki tarah abu-Muawia ne Aamash se bhi ki hai. aur Shoba ne kaha ke mujh ko Sulaiman Aamash ne khabar di ke maine khaisma se suna aur unhon-ne abu-Atiya se, unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna. phir yahi hadis bayan ki."
1551,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne, Madina mein ham bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they Zohar ki Namaz char rakaat padhi aur zul-Hulaifa mein Asr ki Namaz 2 rakaat . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko wahin rahe. subah hui to maqam beda se sawari par baithtey huey Allah Taala ki hamd , uski tasbeeh aur takbeer kahi . phir Haj aur Umra ke liye aik sath ehram baandha aur logon ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath donon ka aik sath ehram baandha (yani Qiraan kya) jab ham Makka aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se (jin logon ne haje-tamattoa' ka ehram baandha tha un) sab ne ehram khol diya. phir aathwiin taareekh mein sab ne Haj ka ehram baandhaa. unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se khadey ho kar bahut se oont nehar kiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eidul-Az'haa ke din) Madina mein bhi 2 chitkabrey seengon waley mendhey zabah kiye they. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke kuchh log us hadis ko yun riwayat kartey hain Ayub se, unhon-ne aik shakhs se, unhon-ne Anas se."
1552,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari poori tarah khadi ho gaee thi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt labbaik pukara .
1553,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab zul-Hulaifa mein subah ki Namaz padh chukey to apni ontni par paalaan lagaaney ka hukm farmaya, sawari laai gaee to aap is par Sawar huey aur jab wo aapko lekar khadi ho gaee to aap khadey ho kar qibla roo ho gaey aur phir labbaik kehna shuru kya yahan tak ke haram mein dakhil ho gaey. wahan pahunch kar aap ne labbaik kehna band kar diya. phir zi tuwa mein tashrif la kar raat wahin guzaarey subah hoti to Namaz padhtey aur ghusl kartey ( phir Makka mein dakhil hotey (aap yaqin ke sath ye jantey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi isi tarah kya tha. Abdul-Waris ki tarah us hadis ko Ismail ne bhi Ayub se riwayat kya. usmein ghusl ka zikr hai."
1554,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab Makka janey ka irada kartey they pahley khushbu ke baghair tel istemal kartey. uske baad masjid zul-Hulaifa mein tashrif latey yahan subah ki Namaz padhtey, phir sawar hotey, jab ontni aapko lekar poori tarah khadi ho jati to ehram baandhtey . phir farmatey ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is tarah kartey dekha tha."
1555,ham Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir they. logon ne dajjal ka zikr kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai ke uski donon aankhon ke darmyan kaafir likha hua hoga. to Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke maine to ye nahi suna. haan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha ke maano mein Musa (Alaihissalam) ko dekh raha hun ke jab aap naley mein utrey to labbaik keh rahe hain.
1556,"ham Hijjatul-wada main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rawaana huey. pahley ham ne Umre ka ehram baandha lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiske sath qurbani ho to usey Umra ke sath Haj ka bhi ehram baandh lena chahiye aisa shakhs darmyan mein halal nahi ho sakta balke Haj aur Umra donon se aik sath halal hoga. main bhi Makka aai thi us waqt main haaiza ho gaee, isliye na Baitullah ka tawaaf kar saki aur na Safa aur Marwa ki saee. maine iske mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shikwa kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apna sar khol daal, kangha kar aur Umra chhod kar Haj ka ehram baandh ley. chunanche maine aisa hi kya phir jab ham Haj se farigh ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey mere bhai Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-Bakar ke sath taneem bhejaa. maine wahan se Umre ka ehram baandha (aur Umra ada kya) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye tumharey us Umra ke badley mein hai. (jisey tum ne chhod diya tha) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke jin logon ne (hijjatul-wadaa mein) sirf Umre ka ehram baandha tha, wo Baitullah ka tawaaf Safa aur Marwa ki saee karke halal ho gaey. phir Mina se wapas honey par doosra tawaaf (yani tawaafe-ziyaara) kya lekin jin logon ne Haj aur Umre ka aik sath ehram baandha tha, unhon-ne sirf aik hi tawaaf kya yani tawaafe-ziyaara kya."
1557,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya tha ke wo apne ehram par qaaim rahiin. unhon-ne Suraqa ka qaul bhi zikr kya tha aur Muhammad-bin-abii-bakar ne ibne-Juraij se yun riwayat kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya Ali! tum ne kis cheez ka ehram baandha hai? unhon-ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jiska ehram baandha ho (usi ka maine bhi baandha hai) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir qurbani kar aur apni usi haalat par ehram jari rakh.
1558,Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yaman se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kis tarah ka ehram baandha hai? unhon-ne kaha ke jis tarah ka Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baandha ho. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar mere sath qurbani na hoti to main halal ho jata.
1559,"mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri qaum ke paas Yaman bheja tha. jab (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par) mein aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Batha mein mulaqat hui. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kiskaa ehram baandha hai? maine kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jiska baandha ho Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya tumharey sath qurbani hai? maine kaha ke nahi, isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya ke main Baitullah ka tawaaf , Safa aur Marwa ki saee karun chunanche main apni qaum ki aik khatun ke paas aaya. unhon-ne mere sar ka kangha kya ya mera sar dhoya. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka zamana aaya to aap ne farmaya ke agar ham Allah ki kitab par amal karein to wo ye hukm deti hai ke Haj aur Umra pura karo. Allah Taala farmata hai ''aur Haj aur Umra pura karo Allah ki raza ke liye. ''aur agar ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat ko lein to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt tak ehram nahi khola jab tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani se faraghat nahi hasil farmai."
1560,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj ke mahinon mein Haj ki raaton main aur Haj ke dinon mein nikley. phir saraf mein ja kar utrey. aap ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba ko khitab farmaya jiske sath qurbani ka janwar na ho aur wo chahta ho ke apne ehram ko sirf Umre ka bana ley to usey aisa kar lena chahiye lekin jiske sath qurbani hai wo aisa na kare. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh ashaab ne us farman par amal kya aur kuchh ne nahi kya. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke kuchh ashaab jo istitaat w hosle waley they (ke wo ehram ke mamnooaat se bach saktey they.) unke sath qurbani ka janwar bhi tha, isliye wo tanha Umra nahi kar saktey they (isliye unhon-ne ehram nahi kholaa) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey to main ro rahi thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke (aey bhuli bhaalii aurat ! tu) ro kyon rahi hai? maine kaha ke maine aap ke apne sahaba se irshad ko sun liya, ab to main Umra na kar sakoongii. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya baat hai? maine kaha, main Namaz padhney ke qaabil na rahi (yani haaiza ho gai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya koi harj nahi. aakhir tum bhi to Adam ki betiyon ki tarah aik aurat ho aur Allah ne tumharey liye bhi wo muqaddar kya hai jo tamam aurton ke liye kya hai. isliye (umra chhod kar) Haj karti reh Allah Taala tumhen jald hi umre ki taufeeq dedega . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ye bayan kya ke ham Haj ke liye nikley. jab ham ( Arafaat se) Mina pahunchey to main paak ho gaee. phir Mina se jab main nikli to Baitullah ka tawaafe-ziyaara kya. aap ne bayan kya ke aakhir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jab wapas honey lagi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wadi Muhassab mein aan kar utrey . ham bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath thahrey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr ko bula kar kaha ke apni behan ko lekar haram se bahar ja aur wahan se Umre ka ehram baandh phir Umra se farigh ho kar tum log yahin wapas aa jao, main tumhara intizar karta rahoonga. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke ham (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hidayat ke mutabiq ( chaley aur jab main aur mere bhai tawaaf se farigh ho liye to main sehrii ke waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchi . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke farigh ho lein? maine kaha haan. tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sathiyon se safar shuru kar dene ke liye kaha, safar shuru ho gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina Munawra wapas ho rahe they. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke jo ( لايضيرک ( hai wo ( ضار يضير ضيراا ) se nikla hai يضور ضورا) bhi istemal hota hai. aur jis riwayat main ( لايضرک ( hai wo ( ضر يضر ضرا‏ ( se nikla hai."
1561,"ham Haj ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley. hamari niyat Haj ke siwa aur kuchh na thi. jab ham Makka pahunchey to (aur logon ne) Baitullah ka tawaaf kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hukm tha ke jo qurbani apne sath na laya ho wo halal ho jaey. chunanche jinke paas qurbani ka janwar nahi tha wo halal ho gaey. (umra ada karne ke baad) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyan qurbani ka janwar nahi ley gaee thin, isliye unhon-ne bhi ehram khol daley . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke main haaiza ho gaee thi isliye Baitullah ka tawaaf na kar saki (yani Umra chhoot gaya aur Haj karti chali gai) jab Muhassab ki raat aaii, maine kaha ya Rasulullah! aur log to Haj aur Umra donon karke wapas ho rahe hain lekin main sirf Haj kar saki hun. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab ham Makka aaey they, to tum tawaaf na kar saki thi? maine kaha ke nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne bhai ke sath taneem tak chali ja aur wahan se Umre ka ehram baandh ( phir Umra ada kar) ham log tumhara falan jagah intizar karengey aur Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke malum hota hai main bhi aap ( logon ( ko rokney ka sabab bin jaaungii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( عقرى حلقى ( kya tu ney yaumun-nahar (Qurbaani ke din) ka tawaaf nahi kya tha? unhon-ne kaha kyon nahi main to tawaaf kar chuki hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir koi harj nahi. chal kooch kar. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke phir meri mulaqat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka se jatey huey uper ke hisse par chadh rahe they aur main nasheb mein utar rahi thi ya ye kaha ke main uper chadh rahi thi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us chadhaao ke baad utar rahe they."
1562,"ham Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chaley. kuchh logon ne Umre ka ehram baandha tha, kuchh ne Haj aur Umra donon ka aur kuchh ne sirf Haj kaa. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (pahley ( sirf Haj ka ehram baandha tha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umra bhi Sharik kar liya, phir jin logon ne Haj ka ehram baandha tha ya Haj aur Umra donon ka, unka ehram dasween taareekh tak na khul saka."
1563,Usman aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko maine dekha hai. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) Haj aur Umra ko aik sath ada karne se roktey they lekin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske bawajud donon ka aik sath ehram baandha aur kaha ( لبيك بعمرة وحجة (aap ne farmaya tha ke main kisi aik shakhs ki baat par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis ko nahi chhod sakta.
1564,"Arab samajhtey they ke Haj ke dinon mein Umra karna poori zameen par sabse bada gunah hai. ye log Muharram ko safar bana letey aur kehtey ke jab oont ki peeth sustaa ley aur is par khub baal ug jayen aur safar ka mahina khatm ho jaey (yani Haj ke din guzar jaaein) to Umra halal hota hai. phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sahaba ke sath chothi ki subah ko Haj ka ehram baandhey huey aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke apne Haj ko Umra bana lein, ye hukm (arab ke puraaney riwaaj ki bina par) aam sahaba par bada bhari guzraa. unhon-ne puchha ya Rasulullah! Umra karke hamarey liye kya cheez halal ho gaii? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tamam cheezein halal ho jaaeingii."
1565,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par Yaman se) hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (mujh ko Umra ke baad) ehram khol dene ka hukm diya.
1566,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se malum kya ya Rasulullah! kya baat hai aur log to Umra karke halal ho gaey lekin aap halal nahi huey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine apne sar ki talbeed (baalon ko jamaaney ke liye aik lesdaar cheez ka iste'maal) ki hai aur apne sath qurbani ka janwar ( qurbani ka janwar ( laya hon isliye main qurbani karne se pahley ehram nahi khol sakta.
1567,"maine Haj aur Umre ka aik sath ehram baandha to kuchh logon ne mujhey mana kya. isliye maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se iske mutaalliq malum kya. aap ne tamatto karne ke liye kaha, phir maine aik shakhs ko dekha ke mujh se keh raha hai'' Haj bhi mabroor hua aur Umra bhi qabool hua '' maine ye khuwab Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko sunaya , to aap ne farmaya ke ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat hai. phir aap ne farmaya ke mere yahan qiyam kar, main apne paas se tumharey liye kuchh muqarrar karke diya karunga. Shoba ne bayan kya ke maine (abu-Jamra se) puchha ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye kyon kya tha? (yani maal kis baat par dene ke liye kaha) unhon-ne bayan kya ke usi khuwab ki wjah se jo maine dekha tha."
1568,"main tamatto ki niyat se Umre ka ehram baandh ke yaume-tarwiya se teen din pahley Makka pahuncha. is par Makka ke kuchh logon ne kaha ab tumhara Haj Makki hoga. main Ata-bin-abi-Ribah ki khidmat mein hazir hua. yahi poochhney ke liye. unhon-ne farmaya ke mujh se Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath wo Haj kya tha jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sath qurbani ke oont laey they (yani hijjatul-wadaa') sahaba ne sirf mufrad Haj ka ehram baandha tha. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke) Umre ka ehram baandh lo aur) Baitullah ke tawaaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee ke baad apne ehram khol dalo aur baal tarashwa lo. yaume-tarwiya tak barabar isi tarah halal raho, phir yaume-tarwiya main Makka hi se Haj ka ehram baandho aur is tarah apne haje-mufrad ko jiski tum ne pahley niyat ki thi, ab usey tamatto bana lo. sahaba ne kaha ke ham usey tamatto kaisey bana saktey hain? ham to Haj ka ehram baandh chukey hain. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis tarah main keh raha hun waisey hi karo. agar mere sath qurbani ka janwar na hoti to khud mein bhi isi tarah karta jis tarah tum se keh raha hun. lekin main kya karun ab mere liye koi cheez us waqt tak halal nahi ho sakti jab tak mere qurbani ke janwaron ki qurbani na ho jaey. chunanche sahaba ne aap ke hukm ki ta'meel ki. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke abu-Shihaab ki us hadis ke siwa aur koi marfoo' hadis marwi (bayan) nahi hai."
1569,Usman aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Asfan aaey to unmein aapasii tamatto ke silsiley mein ikhtilaf hua to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke jisko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya hai us se aap kyon rok rahe hain? is par Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke mujhey apne haal par rehney do. ye dekh kar Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Haj aur Umra donon ka ehram aik sath baandhaa.
1570,jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aaey to ham ne Haj ki labbaik pukaarii. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ham ne usey Umra bana liya.
1571,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein ham ne tamatto kya tha aur khud Quran mein tamatto ka hukm nazil hua tha. ab aik shakhs ne apni raey se jo chaha keh diya.
1572,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se Haj mein tamatto ke mutaalliq puchha gaya. aap ne farmaya ke Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par muhajireen Ansar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon aur ham sab ne ehram baandha tha. jab ham Makka aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne ehram ko Haj aur Umra donon ke liye kar lo lekin jo log qurbani ka janwar apne sath laey hain. (wo Umra karne ke baad halal nahi hongey) chunanche ham ne Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa w Marwa ki saee kar li to apna ehram khol daala aur ham apni beeviyon ke paas gaey aur siley huey kapdey pahney . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke jiske sath qurbani ka janwar hai wo us waqt tak halal nahi ho sakta jab tak qurbani ka janwar apni jagah na pahunch ley (yani qurbani na ho ley) hamein (jinhon ne qurbani ka janwar sath nahi liya tha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aathwiin taareekh ki Sham ko hukm diya ke ham Haj ka ehram baandh lein. phir jab ham Haj ki adaayegi se farigh ho gaey to ham ne aa kar Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee ki, phir hamara Haj pura ho gaya aur ab qurbani ham par lazim hui. jaisa ke Allah Taala ka irshad hai ''jisey qurbani ka janwar muyassar ho (to wo qurbani karey) aur agar kisi ko qurbani ki taqat na ho to teen rozey Haj main aur saat (7) din ghar wapas honey par rakhey (qurbaanii mein) bakri bhi kafi hai. to logon ne Haj aur Umra donon ibaadatein aik hi saal mein aik sath ada kin. kyonke Allah Taala ne khud apni kitab mein ye hukm nazil kya tha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par khud amal karke tamam logon ke liye jaaiz qarar diya tha. albatta Makka ke baashindon ka us se istisnaa hai. kyonke Allah Taala ka farman hai ''ye hukm un logon ke liye hai jinke ghar waley masjide-Haraam ke paas rehney waley na hon'' aur Haj ke jin mahinon ka Quran mein zikr hai wo shawwaal, Zi-Qaada aur Zil-Hijja hain. un mahinon mein jo koi bhi tamatto karey wo ya qurbani de ya agar maqdoor na ho to rozey rakhey aur) رفث (ka mana hambistari (ya fahash baatein) aur) فسوق ( gunah aur) جدال ( logon se jhagadnaa ."
1573,"jab Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) haram ki sarhad ke qareeb pahunchtey to talbiya kehna band kar detey. raat zi tuwa mein guzaartey, subah ki Namaz wahin padhtey aur ghusl kartey ( phir Makka mein dakhil hotey (aap bayan kartey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi isi tarah kya kartey they."
1574,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zi tuwa mein raat guzari. phir jab subah hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huey. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi isi tarah kartey they.
1575,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein buland ghaati (yani jannatul-Muallaa) ki taraf se dakhil hotey aur nikaltey ''saniyatus-Sufla'' ki taraf se yani nichey ki ghaati ki taraf se.
1576,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( الثنية العليا ( yani maqam kadaa ki taraf se dakhil hotey jo Batha mein hai aur) الثنية السفلى‏ .) ki taraf se nikaltey they yani nichey wali ghaati ki taraf se. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha Musaddad ke naam se they yani Musaddad ke mana arabii zaban mein mazbut aur durust ke hain to hadis ki riwayat mein mazbut aur durust they aur maine Yahya bin muaiyan se suna wo kehtey hain maine Yahya qattaan se suna, wo kehtey they agar main Musaddad ke ghar ja kar unko hadis sunaya karta to wo iske laaiq they aur meri kitaabein hadis ki mere paas rahen ya Musaddad ke paas mujhey kuchh parwah nahi. maano Yahya qattaan ne Musaddad ki behad tareef ki."
1577,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein tashrif laey to uper ki buland taraf se Shahar ke andar dakhil huey aur (Makka se) wapas jab gaey to nichey ki taraf se nikal gaey.
1578,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka ke mauqe par Shahar mein kadaa ki taraf se dakhil huey aur kadaa ki taraf se nikley jo Makka ke buland taraf hai.
1579,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka mauqe par dakhil hotey waqt Makka ke oopri ilaqa kadaa se dakhil huey. Hisham ne bayan kya ke Urwa agarche kadaa aur kudaa donon taraf se dakhil hotey they lekin aksar kudaa se dakhil hotey kyonke ye rasta unke ghar se qareeb tha.
1580,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka ke mauqe par Makka ke oopri ilaqe kadaa ki taraf se dakhil huey they. lekin Urwa aksar Kudaa ki taraf se dakhil hotey they kyonke ye rasta unke ghar se qareeb tha.
1581,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka ke mauqe par kadaa se dakhil huey they. Urwa khud halaanki donon taraf se (kadaa aur Kudaa) dakhil hotey lekin aksar aap Kudaa ki taraf se dakhil hotey they kyonke ye rasta unke ghar se qareeb tha. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke kadaa aur Kudaa 2 maqamat ke naam hain.
1582,( zamana jahiliyat mein) jab Kaba ki tameer hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bhi patthar utha kar la rahe they. Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke apna tehband utaar kar kaandhey par daal lo (taake patthar uthaney mein takleef na ho) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa kya to nangey hotey hi behosh ho kar aap zameen par gir padey aur aap ki aankhen aasman ki taraf lag gaiin. aap kehney lagey mujhey mera tehband de do. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey mazbut baandh liya.
1583,aur unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak biwi Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke tujhey malum hai jab teri qaum ne Kaba ki tameer ki to buniyaade-Ibraaheem ko chhod diya tha. maine arz kya ya Rasulullah ! phir aap buniyaade-Ibraaheem par usko kyon nahi bana detey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tumhari qaum ka zamana kufr se bilkul nazdeek na hota to main beshak aisa kar deta. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai (aur yaqinan Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sachchii hain) to main samajhta hun yahi wjah thi jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hateem se muttasil jo diiwaaron ke koney hain unko nahi choomtey they. kyonke khaana Kaba Ibraaheemii buniyaadon par pura na hua tha.
1584,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke kya Hateem bhi Baitullah mein dakhil hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, phir maine puchha ke phir logon ne usey Kabey mein kyon nahi shamil kya? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab diya ke tumhari qaum ke paas kharch ki kami pad gaee thi. phir maine puchha ke ye darwaza kyon uncha banaayaa? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye bhi tumhari qaum hi ne kya taake jisey chaahein andar aaney dein aur jisey chaahein rok dein. agar tumhari qaum ki jahiliyat ka zamana taaza-taaza na hota aur mujhey iska khof na hota ke unke dil bigad jaeinge to us Hateem ko bhi main Kaba mein shamil kar deta aur Kaba ka darwaza zameen ke barabar kar detaa."
1585,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya, agar tumhari qaum ka zamana kufr se abhi taaza na hota to main khaana Kaba ko tod kar usey Ibrahim ki buniyad par banata kyonke Quraish ne usmein kami kar di hai. usmein aik darwaza aur us darwazey ke muqabil rakhta . abu-Muawia ne kaha ham se Hisham ne bayan kya. hadis main ( Khalaf ( se darwaza murad hai."
1586,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Aaisha ! agar teri qaum ka zamana jahiliyat abhi taaza na hota, to main Baitullah ko giraaney ka hukm de deta taake ( nai tameer mein) us hisse ko bhi dakhil kar dun jo us se bahar reh gaya hai aur uski kursi zameen ke barabar kar dun aur uske 2 darwazey bana dun, aik mashriq main aur aik maghrib mein. is tarah Ibrahim ki buniyad par uski tameer ho jati. Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ka Kaba ko giraaney se yahi maqsad tha. Yazeed ne bayan kya ke main us waqt maujood tha jab Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey giraayaa tha aur uski nai tameer karke Hateem ko iske andar kar diya tha. maine Ibrahim ki tameer ke paaey bhi dekhey jo oont ki kohan ki tarah they. Jareer-bin-Haazim ne kaha ke maine unse poochha, unki jagah kahan hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke main abhi dikhaataa hun. chunanche main unke sath Hateem mein gaya aur aap ne aik jagah ki taraf ishara karke kaha ke ye wo jagah hai. Jarir ne kaha ke maine andaza lagaya ke wo jagah Hateem mein se chh hath hogi ya aisi hi kuchh ."
1587,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka par farmaya tha ke Allah Taala ne us Shahar (Makka) ko hurmat wala banaya hai (yani izzat di hai) to iske (darakhton ke) kaantey tak bhi nahi kaatey ja saktey yahan ke shikar bhi nahi hankaaey ja saktey aur unke ilawa jo elaan karke (Maalik tak pahunchaney ka irada rakhtey hon) koi shakhs yahan ki girii-padii cheez bhi nahi utha sakta hai.
1588,"unhon-ne puchha ya Rasulullah ! aap Makka mein kya apne ghar mein qiyam farmaaeingey. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Aqeel ne hamarey liye mahalla ya makan chhoda hi Kab hai. (sab bech-khoch kar barabar kar diye ( Aqeel aur taalib , abu-Taalib ke waaris huey they. Jafar aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko waraasat mein kuchh nahi mila tha, kyonke ye donon musalman ho gaey they aur Aqeel (Raziallahu anhu) (ibtidaa mein) aur taalib Islam nahi laey they. usi buniyad par Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they ke musalman kaafir ka waaris nahi hota. ibne-Shahab ne kaha ke log Allah Taala ke us irshad se daleel letey hain ke ''jo log eman laaey, hijrat ki aur apne maal aur jaan ke sath Allah ki raah mein jihad kya aur wo log jinhoney panah di aur madad ki, wahi aik doosrey ke waaris hongey.''"
1589,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab ( Mina se laut'tey huey Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par) Makka aaney ka irada kya to farmaya ke kal inshaAllah hamara qiyam isi khaif bani kinaana (yani Mohassab) mein hoga jahan ( Quraish ne) kufr par adey rehney ki qism khaaii thi.
1590,"giyaarahwen ki subah ko jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Mina mein they, to ye farmaya tha ke kal ham khaif banii-kinaana mein qiyam karengey jahan Quraish ne kufr ki himaayat ki qism khaaii thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad Muhassab se thi kyonke yahin Quraish aur kinaana ne banu-Haashim aur banu-Abdul-Muttalib ya ( rawi ne) banu-Muttalib (kaha (ke khilaf Halaf uthaya tha ke jab tak wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unke hawale na kar dein, unke yahan shadi biyaah na karengey aur na unse khareed w farokht karengey aur Sulaamaa-bin-Rooh ne Aqeel aur Yahya bin Suhak se riwayat kya, unse imam Auzai ne bayan kya ke mujhey ibne-Shahab ne khabar di, unhon-ne (apni riwayat mein) banu-Haashim aur banu-muttalib kaha, abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke banu-muttalib zyada sahi hai."
1591,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke '' Kaba ko 2 patlii pindliyon wala aik haqeer habshi tabah kar dega.''
1592,Ramazan (ke rozey ( farz honey se pahley musalman Aashooraa ka roza rakhtey they. Aashooraa hi ke din ( jahiliyat mein) Kaba par ghilaaf chadhaayaa jata tha. phir jab Allah Taala ne Ramazan farz kar diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se farmaya ke '' ab jiska ji chahey Aashooraa ka roza rakhey aur jiska ji chahey chhod de. ''
1593,Baitullah ka Haj aur Umra Yaajooj aur Maajooj ke nikalney ke baad bhi hota rahega. Abdullah-bin-Ubai Utba ke sath us hadis ko Aban aur Imran ne Qatada se riwayat kya aur Abdur-Rehman ne Shoba ke waaste se yun bayan kya ke qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahi hogi jab tak Baitullah ka Haj band na ho jaey. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke pehli riwayat zyada rawiyon ne ki hai aur Qatada ne Abdullah-bin Utba se suna aur Abdullah ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna.
1594,main Sheba ke sath Kaba mein kursi par betha hua tha to Sheba ne farmaya ke isi jagah baith kar umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (eik martaba ( farmaya ke mera irada ye hota hai ke Kaba ke andar jitna sona chandi hai usey na chhodun ( jisey zamana jahiliyat mein kuffaar ne jama kya tha) balke sab ko nikal kar) musalmanon mein) taqseem kar dun. maine kaha ke aap ke sathiyon (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne to aisa nahi kya. unhon-ne farmaya ke main bhi unhein ki pairwi kar raha hun (isii liye main iske hath nahi lagaataa) .
1595,'maano meri nazron ke samney wo patlii taangon wala siyah aadmi hai jo khaana Kaba ke eik-eik patthar ko ukhaad phainkega.''
1596,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Kaba ko 2 patlii pindliyon wala habshi kharaab karega. ''
1597,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) hajre-Aswad ke paas aaey aur usey bosa diya aur farmaya ''main khub janta hun ke to sirf aik patthar hai, na kisi ko nuqsan pahuncha sakta hai na nafa . agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tujhey bosa detey huey main na dekhta to main bhi kabhi tujhey bosa na deta.''"
1598,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Usama-bin-Zaid aur Bilal w Usman bin abi Talha (Raziallahu anhu) charon khaana Kaba ke andar gaey aur andar se darwaza band kar liya. phir jab darwaza khola to main pahlaa shakhs tha jo andar gaya. meri mulaqat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se hui. maine puchha ke kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (andar ( Namaz padhi hai? unhon-ne batlaya ke '' haan ! donon yamnii sutunon ke darmyan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi hai.''
1599,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab Kaba ke andar dakhil hotey to samney ki taraf chaltey aur darwaza peeth ki taraf chhod detey. aap isi tarah chaltey rahtey aur jab samney ki diwar taqriban teen hath reh jati to Namaz padhtey they. is tarah aap us jagah Namaz padhney ka ehtimaam kartey they jiske mutaalliq Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se malum hua tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahin Namaz padhi thi. lekin usmein koi harj nahi Kaba mein jis jagah bhi koi chahey Namaz padh ley.
1600,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umra kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kaba ka tawaaf karke maqaame-Ibraaheem ke peechhey 2 rakatein padhin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kuchh log they jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aur logon ke darmyan aad baney huey they. unmein se aik sahib ne ibne-abii-Aaufii se puchha kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba ke andar tashrif le gaey they, to unhon-ne bataya ke'' nahi.''"
1601,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab (fatah Makka ke din) tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kaba ke andar janey se isliye inkar farmaya ke usmein but rakhey huey they. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya aur wo nikaley gaey, logon ne Ibrahim aur Ismail (Alaihissalam) ke but bhi nikaaley. unke hathon mein faal nikalney ke teer de rakhey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah un mushrikon ko ghaarat karey, Allah ki qism unhein achi tarah malum tha ke un buzurgon ne teer se faal kabhi nahi nikaalii. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba ke andar tashrif le gaey aur charon taraf takbeer kahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne andar Namaz nahi padhi."
1602,"( umratul-qazaa 7 hijri mein) jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka) tashrif laey to mushrikon ne kaha ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aaey hain, unke sath aisey log aaey hain jinhein yasrib (Madina Munawra (ke bukhar ne kamzor kar diya hai. isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke tawaaf ke pahley teen chakkaron mein ramal ( tez chalnaa jis se izhaare-quwwat ho) karein aur donon Yamani ruknon ke darmyan mamool (routine) k mutabiq chalein aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye hukm nahi diya ke sab pheron mein ramal karein isliye ke un par aasani ho."
1603,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka tashrif latey to pahley tawaaf shuru kartey waqt hajre-Aswad ko bosa detey aur saat (7) chakkaron mein se pahley teen chakkaron mein ramal kartey they.
1604,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahley teen chakkaron mein ramal kya aur Baqiiya char chakkaron mein mamool (routine) ke mutabiq chaley, Haj aur Umra donon mein. Suraij ke sath us hadis ko Leis ne riwayat kya hai. kaha ke mujh se kaseer-bin-Farqad ne bayan kya, unse Naafe ne aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se."
1605,Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne hajre-Aswad ko khitab karke farmaya ''b-khudaa mujhey khub malum hai ke to sirf aik patthar hai jo na koi nafa pahuncha sakta hai na nuqsan aur agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tujhey bosa detey na dekha hota to main kabhi bosa na detaa.'' iske baad aap ne bosa diya. phir farmaya'' aur ab hamein ramal ki bhi kya zarurat hai. ham ne iske zariey mushrikon ko apni quwwat dikhai thi to Allah ne unko tabah kar diya. ''phir farmaya'' jo amal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya hai usey ab chhodnaa bhi ham pasand nahi kartey.''
1606,jab se maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko un donon rukn Yamani ko choomtey huey dekha maine bhi iske choomney ko chahe sakht halaat hon ya narm nahi chhodaa. maine Naafe se puchha kya ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) un donon yamnii ruknon ke darmyan mamool (routine) ke mutabiq chaltey they? to unhon-ne bataya ke aap mamool (routine) ke mutabiq isliye chaltey they taake hajre-Aswad ko chhooney mein aasani rahe.
1607,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par apni ontni par tawaaf kya tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hajre-Aswad ka istilaam aik chhadi ke zariey kar rahe they aur us chhadi ko choomtey they. aur Yunus ke sath us hadis ko darawardi ne Zohri ke bhatijey se riwayat kya aur unhon-ne apne chacha (Zohri ( se.
1608,"Abul-Sha'a-Sa'a ne kaha Baitullah ke kisi bhi hisse se bhala kon parhez kar sakta hai. aur Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) charon ruknon ka istilaam kartey they, is par Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke ham un 2 arkaane-Shaamii aur Iraaqii ka istilaam nahi kartey to Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Baitullah ka koi Juz aisa nahi jisey chhod diya jaey aur Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) bhi tamam arkaan ka istilaam kartey they."
1609,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sirf donon Yamani arkaan ka istilaam kartey dekha.
1610,Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne hajre-Aswad ko bosa diya aur phir farmaya ke ''agar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tujhey bosa detey na dekhta to main kabhi tujhey bosa na detaa.''
1611,aik shakhs ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hajre-Aswad ke bosa dene ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne batlaya ke ''maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko usko bosa detey dekha hai.'' is par us shakhs ne kaha agar hujoom ho jaey aur main aajiz ho jaun to kya karun? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ''is agar wagar ko Yaman mein ja kar rakho maine to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap usko bosa detey they.''
1612,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik ontni par (sawaar ho kar Kaba ka ( tawaaf kar rahe they aur jab bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hajre-Aswad ke samney pahunchtey to kisi cheez se uski taraf ishara kartey they.
1613,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ka tawaaf aik ontni par Sawar reh kar kya. jab bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hajre-Aswad ke samney pahunchtey to kisi cheez se uski taraf ishara kartey aur takbeer kehtey. Khalid Tahan ke sath us hadis ko Ibraaheem-bin-tahmaan ne bhi Khalid hazaa se riwayat kya hai.
1614,"maine Urwa se ( Haj ka masla ( puchha to unhon-ne farmaya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey khabar di thi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab (Makka) tashrif laey to sabse pahlaa kaam Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye kya ke wuzu kya phir tawaaf kya aur tawaaf karne se Umra nahi hua. iske baad Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi isi tarah Haj kya. phir Urwa ne kaha ke maine apne walid Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Haj kya, unhon-ne bhi sabse pahley tawaaf kya. muhajireen aur Ansar ko bhi maine isi tarah kartey dekha tha. meri walida ( Asma binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bhi mujhey bataya ke unhon-ne apni behan ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (aur Zuber aur falan-falan ke sath Umre ka ehram baandha tha. jab un logon ne hajre-Aswad ko bosa de liya to ehram khol daala tha."
1615,"maine Urwa se ( Haj ka masla ( puchha to unhon-ne farmaya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey khabar di thi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab (Makka) tashrif laey to sabse pahlaa kaam Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye kya ke wuzu kya phir tawaaf kya aur tawaaf karne se Umra nahi hua. iske baad Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi isi tarah Haj kya. phir Urwa ne kaha ke maine apne walid Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Haj kya, unhon-ne bhi sabse pahley tawaaf kya. muhajireen aur Ansar ko bhi maine isi tarah kartey dekha tha. meri walida ( Asma binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bhi mujhey bataya ke unhon-ne apni behan ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (aur Zuber aur falan-falan ke sath Umre ka ehram baandha tha. jab un logon ne hajre-Aswad ko bosa de liya to ehram khol daala tha."
1616,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Makka) aaney ke baad sabse pahley Haj aur Umre ka tawaaf kya tha. iske teen chakkaron mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saee ( ramal ( ki aur baqi char mein mamool (routine) ke mutabiq chaley. phir tawaaf ki 2 rakaat Namaz padhi aur Safa Marwa ki saee ki.
1617,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Baitullah ka pahlaa tawaaf (yani tawaaf qudoom) kartey to iske teen chakkaron mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) daud kar chaltey aur char mein mamool (routine) ke muwafiq chaltey phir jab Safa aur Marwa ki saee kartey to ''batane-Maseel'' ( wadi ( mein daud kar chaltey .
1618,"jab ibne-Hishaam (jab wo Hisham bin Abdul-Malik ki taraf se Makka ka Hakim tha) ne aurton ko mardon ke sath tawaaf karne se mana kar diya to usse unhon-ne kaha ke tum kis daleel par aurton ko us se mana kar rahe ho? jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak beeviyon ne mardon ke sath tawaaf kya tha. ibne-Juraij ne puchha ye parda (ki aayat nazil honey) ke baad ka waqia hai ya us se pahley kaa? unhon-ne kaha meri umr ki qasam! maine unhein parde (ki aayat nazil honey) ke baad dekha. is par ibne-Juraij ne puchha ke phir mard-aurat mil jul jatey they. unhon-ne farmaya ke ikhtilat (milap) nahi hota tha, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) mardon se alag reh kar aik alag koney mein tawaaf karti thin, unke sath mil kar nahi karti thin. aik aurat (waqraa naamii) ne unse kaha ummul-momeneen! chaliye (hajre-Aswad ko) bosa dein. to aap ne inkar kar diya aur kaha to ja choom, main nahi choomtii aur paak beeviyan raat mein parda karke nikalti thin ke pahchaanii na jaatiin aur mardon ke sath tawaaf karti thin. albatta auratein jab Kaba ke andar jana chaahatiin to andar janey se pahley bahar khadi ho jaatiin aur mard bahar aa jatey (to wo andar jaatiin) main aur Ubaid-bin-Umair Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein us waqt hazir huey jab aap Sabeer ( pahaad ( par thahrii hui thin, (jo Muzdalfa mein hai) ibne-Juraij ne kaha ke maine Ata se puchha ke us waqt parda kis cheez se tha? Ata ne bataya ke aik turki quba mein thahrii hui thin. is par parda padaa hua tha. hamarey aur unke darmyan iske siwa aur koi cheez rukawat na thi. us waqt maine dekha ke unke badan par aik gulaabii rang ka kurta tha."
1619,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apne bimar honey ki shikayat ki (ke main paidal tawaaf nahi kar saktii) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sawari par chadh kar aur logon se alehda reh kar tawaaf kar ley. chunanche maine aam logon se alag reh kar tawaaf kya. us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba ke pahlu mein Namaz padh rahe they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Sura Toor) qirat kar rahe they.
1620,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba ka tawaaf kartey huey aik aisey shakhs ke paas se guzrey jisne apna hath aik doosrey shakhs ke hath se tasma ya rassii ya kisi aur cheez se baandh rakha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se usey kaat diya aur phir farmaya ke ''agar sath hi chalnaa hai to hath pakad ke chalo. ''
1621,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke aik shakhs Kaba ka tawaaf rassii ya kisi aur cheez ke zariey kar raha hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey kaat diya.
1622,Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne us Haj ke mauqe par jiska ameer Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein banaya tha. unhein dasween taareekh ko aik majma' ke samney ye elaan karne ke liye bheja tha ke us saal ke baad koi mushrik Haj Baitullah nahi kar sakta aur na koi shakhs nangaa reh kar tawaaf kar sakta hai.
1623,"ham se Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke ham se Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya, unse Amr ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke ham ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke kya koi Umra mein Safa-Marwa ki saee se pahle apni bevi se ham-bistar ho sakta hai? unhone kaha ki Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur Kaba ka tawaaf saat chakkaron se pura kiya. phir maqaame-Ibraaheem ke peechhey do rakaat Namaz padhi phir Safa-Marwa ki saee kii. phir Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Farmaya ke ""tumhaare liye Rasulullah k tareeqe mein behtreen namoona hai."""
1624,Safa Marwa ki saee se pahley apni biwi ke qareeb bhi na jaey.
1625,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka tashrif laey aur saat (7) (chakkaron ke saath) tawaaf kya. phir Safa Marwa ki saee ki. us saee ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba us waqt tak nahi gaey jab tak Arafaat se wapas na lautey.
1626,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shikayat ki. (doosri sanad) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke mujh se Muhammad-bin-harab ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke ham se Abu-Marwaan Yahyaa-ibn-abii-Zakariiyaa ghassaanii ne bayan kya, unse Hisham ne, unse Urwa ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Makka mein they aur wahan se chalney ka irada hua to Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Kaba ka tawaaf nahi kya aur wo bhi rawaangii ka irada rakhti thin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke jab subah ki Namaz khadi ho aur log Namaz padhney mein mashghool ho jayen to tum apni ontni par tawaaf kar lenaa. chunanche Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne aisa hi kya aur unhon-ne bahar nikalney tak tawaaf ki Namaz nahi padhi."
1627,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka mein) tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaana Kaba ka saat (7) chakkaron se tawaaf kya aur maqaame-Ibraaheem ke peechhey 2 rakaat Namaz padhi phir Safa ki taraf (saee karne) gaey aur Allah Taala ne farmaya hai ke tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi behtreen namoona hai.
1628,kuchh logon ne subah ki Namaz ke baad Kaba ka tawaaf kya. phir aik waz (nasihat) karne waley ke paas baith gaey aur jab suraj nikalney laga to wo log Namaz (tawaaf ki 2 rak'at) padhney ke liye khadey ho gaey. is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne (naa-gawaarii ke saath) farmaya jab se ye log baithey they aur jab wo waqt aaya ke jis mein Namaz makruh hai to Namaz ke liye khadey ho gaey.
1629,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) suraj tuloo hotey aur ghurub hotey waqt Namaz padhney se roktey they.
1630,aap fajr ki Namaz ke baad tawaaf kar rahe they aur phir aap ne 2 rakaat (tawaaf ki) Namaz padhi.
1631,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bhi unke ghar aatey (asr ke baad) to ye 2 rakaat zaroor padhtey they.
1632,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ka tawaaf oont par Sawar ho kar kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bhi (tawaaf kartey huey) hajre-Aswad ke nazdeek aatey to apne hath ko aik cheez (chhadii) se ishara kartey aur takbeer kehtey.
1633,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shikayat ki ke main bimar ho gaee hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir logon ke peechhey se Sawar ho kar tawaaf kar ley. chunanche maine jab tawaaf kya to us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Baitullah ke pahlu mein (namaz ke andar) (Sura Toor) ki qirat kar rahe they.
1634,Abbaas-bin-Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apne pani (Zamzam ka haajiyon ko) pilaaney ke liye Mina ke dinon main Makka thaharney ki ijazat chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko ijazat de di.
1635,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pani pilaaney ki jagah (zamzam ke paas) tashrif laey aur pani maanga (Haj ke mauqe par) Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke fazal! apni maa ke yahan ja aur unke yahan se khajoor ka sharbat laa. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey (yahii) pani pulaaw. Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ya Rasulullah! har shakhs apna hath usmein daal deta hai. iske bawajud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) yahi kehtey rahe ke mujhey ( yahi (pani pilaao. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani piyaa phir zamzam ke qareeb aaey. log kuwein se pani kheench rahe they aur kaam kar rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unhein dekh kar) farmaya kaam kartey jao ke aik achchhey kaam par lagey huey ho. phir farmaya (agar ye khayal na hota ke aainda log) tumhen pareshan kar dengey to main bhi utartaa aur rassii apne is par rakh letaa. murad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki shana se thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf ishara karke kaha tha.
1636,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab main Makka mein tha to meri (ghar ki) chhat khuli aur Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) nazil huey. unhon-ne mera Sina chaak kya aur usey zamzam ke pani se dhoya. iske baad aik soney ka tasht laey jo hikmat aur eman se bharaa hua tha. usey unhon-ne mere seeney mein daal diya aur phir Sina band kar diya. ab wo mujhey hath se pakad kar aasmaane-duniyaa ki taraf ley chaley. aasman duniya ke darogha se Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha darwaza kholo. unhon-ne malum kya kon sahib hain? kaha Jibraaiil.
1637,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zamzam ka pani pilaya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pani khadey ho kar piyaa tha. Aasim ne bayan kya ke Ikrima ne qism kha kar kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us din oont par Sawar they.
1638,Hijjatul-wada mein ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (Madina se) nikley aur ham ne Umre ka ehram baandhaa. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiske sath qurbani ka janwar ho wo Haj aur Umra donon ka aik sath ehram baandhey . aisey log donon ke ehram se aik sath halal hongey. mein bhi Makka aai thi lekin mujhey haiz aa gaya tha. isliye jab hamne Haj ada kar liya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey Abdur-Rehman ke sath taneem ki taraf bhejaa. maine wahan se Umre ka ehram baandhaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye tumharey us Umre ke badle mein hai (jisey tum ne haiz ki wjah se chhod diya tha) jin logon ne Umre ka ehram baandha tha unhon-ne saee ke baad ehram khol diya aur doosra tawaaf Mina se waapsii par kya lekin jin logon ne Haj aur Umre ka ehram aik sath baandha tha unhon-ne sirf aik tawaaf kya.
1639,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ladkey Abdullah bin-Abdullah unke yahan gaey. Haj ke liye sawari ghar mein khadi hui thi. unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey khatrah hai ke us saal musalmanon mein aapas mein ladai ho jaeygi aur aapko wo Baitullah se rok dengey. isliye agar aap na jatey to behtar hota. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi tashrif le gaey they (Umra karne suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par) aur kuffaare-Quraish ne aapko Baitullah tak pahunchne se rok diya tha. isliye agar mujhey bhi rok diya gaya to main bhi wahi kaam karunga jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha aur tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi behtreen namoona hai. phir aap ne farmaya ke main tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine apne Umre ke sath Haj (apne uper ( wajib kar liya hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir aap Makka aaey aur donon Umra aur Haj ke liye aik hi tawaaf kya
1640,jis saal Hajjaj Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke muqaabley mein ladney aaya tha. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jab us saal Haj ka irada kya to aap se kaha gaya ke musalmanon mein aapasii jang honey wali hai aur ye bhi khatrah hai ke aapko Haj se rok diya jaey. aap ne farmaya tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi behtreen namoona hai. aisey waqt mein main bhi wahi kaam karunga jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha. tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine apne uper Umra wajib kar liya hai. phir aap chaley aur jab beda ke maidan mein pahunchey to aap ne farmaya ke Haj aur Umra to aik hi tarah ke hain. main tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine apne Umra ke sath Haj bhi wajib kar liya hai. aap ne aik qurbani bhi sath ley li jo maqam qudaid se kharidi thi. iske siwa aur kuchh nahi kya. dasween taareekh se pahley na aap ne qurbani ki na kisi aisi cheez ko apne liye jaaiz kya jis se ( ehram ki wjah se) aap ruk gaey they. na sar mundwaayaa na baal tarashwaaey dasween taareekh mein aap ne qurbani ki aur baal mundwaaey . aap ka yahi khayal tha ke aap ne aik tawaaf se Haj aur Umra donon ka tawaaf ada kar liya hai. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi isi tarah kya tha.
1641,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jaisa ke malum hai Haj kya tha. mujhey Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne iske mutaalliq khabar di ke jab aap Makka muazzama aaey to sabse pahlaa kaam ye kya ke aap ne wuzu kya, phir Kaba ka tawaaf kya. ye aap ka Umra nahi tha. iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Haj kya aur aap ne bhi sabse pahley Kaba ka tawaaf kya jabke ye aap ka bhi Umra nahi tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi isi tarah kya. phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Haj kya maine dekha ke sabse pahley aap ne bhi Kaba ka tawaaf kya. aap ka bhi ye Umra nahi tha. phir Muawiya aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka zamana aaya. phir maine apne walid Zubair-bin-Awaam (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bhi Haj kya. ye (sarey akaabir) pahley Kaba hi ke tawaaf se shuru kartey they jabke ye Umra nahi hota tha. iske baad muhajireen w Ansar ko bhi maine dekha ke wo bhi isi tarah kartey rahe aur unka bhi ye Umra nahi hota tha. aakhiri zaat jisey maine is tarah kartey dekha, wo Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki thi. unhon-ne bhi Umra nahi kya tha. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) abhi maujood hain lekin unse log iske mutaalliq poochhtey nahi. isi tarah jo hazraat guzar gaey, unka bhi Makka mein dakhil hotey hi sabse pahlaa qadam tawaaf ke ley uthtaa tha. phir ye bhi ehram nahi kholtey they. maine apni walida ( Asma binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) (aur khala (Aaisha siddiiqa (Raziallahu anhu)) ko bhi dekha ke jab wo aatiin to sabse pahley tawaaf kartin aur ye iske baad ehram nahi kholtii thin."
1642,unhon-ne apni behan aur Zuber aur falan-falan (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Umra kya hai ye sab log hajre-Aswad ka bosa ley letey to Umre ka ehram khol detey.
1643,"maine Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke Allah Taala ke us farman ke barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai (jo sura al-Baqara mein hai ke) ''Safaa aur Marwa Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein se hain. isliye jo Baitullah ka Haj ya Umra karey uske liye unka tawaaf karne mein koi gunah nahin''. qism Allah ki phir to koi harj na hona chahiye agar koi Safa aur Marwa ki saee na karni chaahey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya bhateejey! tum ne ye buri baat kahi. Allah ka matlab ye hota to Quran mein yun utartaa'' unke tawaaf na karne mein koi gunah nahin'' baat ye hai ke ye aayat to Ansar ke liye utri thi jo Islam se pahley manaat but ke naam par jo Mushallal mein rakha hua tha aur jiski ye puja kya kartey they. ehram baandhtey they. ye log jab (zamaana jahiliyat mein) ehram baandhtey to Safa Marwa ki saee ko achchha nahi khayal kartey they. ab jab Islam laey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq puchha aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah! ham Safa aur Marwa ki saee achi nahi samajhtey they. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai ke Safa aur Marwa donon Allah ki nishaniyan hain aakhir aayat tak. Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un 2 pahadon ke darmyan saee ki sunnat jari ki hai. isliye kisi ke liye munasib nahi hai ke usey tark kar de. unhon-ne kaha ke phir maine iska zikr Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman se kya to unhon-ne farmaya ke maine to ye ilmi baat ab tak nahi suni thi, balke maine bahut se ashaab ilm se to ye suna hai ke wo yun kehtey they ke Arab ke log un logon ke siwa jinka Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne zikr kya jo manaat ke liye ehram baandhtey they sab Safaa-Marwa ka phera kya kartey they. aur jab Allah ne Quran sharif mein Baitullah ke tawaaf ka zikr farmaya aur Safa Marwa ka zikr nahi kya to wo log kehney lagey ya Rasulullah! ham to jahiliyat ke zamane mein Safa aur Marwa ka phera kya kartey they aur ab Allah ne Baitullah ke tawaaf ka zikr to farmaya lekin Safa Marwa ka zikr nahi kya to kya Safa Marwa ki saee karne mein ham par kuchh gunah hoga? tab Allah ne ye aayat utaarii.'' Safaa-Marwa Allah ki nishaniyan hain aakhir aayat tak.'' Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main sunta hun ke ye aayat donon firqon ke baab mein utri hai yani us firqey ke baab mein jo jahiliyat ke zamaney mein Safaa-Marwa ka tawaaf bura janta tha aur uske baab mein jo jahiliyat ke zamaney mein Safa Marwa ka tawaaf kya kartey they. phir musalman honey ke baad iska karna us wjah se ke Allah ne Baitullah ke tawaaf ka zikr kya aur Safa w Marwa ka nahi kya, bura samjhey. yahan tak ke Allah ne Baitullah ke tawaaf ke baad unke tawaaf ka bhi zikr farma diya."
1644,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pahlaa tawaaf kartey to iske teen chakkaron mein ramal kartey aur Baqiiya char mein mamool (routine) ke mutabiq chaltey aur jab Safa aur Marwa ki saee kartey to aap naley ke nasheb mein douda kartey they. Ubaidullah ne kaha maine Naafe se poochha, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab rukne-Yamaanii ke paas pahunchtey to kya mamool (routine) ke mutabiq chalney lagtey they? unhon-ne farmaya ke nahi. albatta agar rukn Yamani par hujoom hota to hajre-Aswad ke paas aa kar aap aahista chalney lagtey kyonke wo baghair choomey usko nahi chhodtey they."
1645,"ham ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aik aisey shakhs ke mutaalliq puchha jo Umre mein Baitullah ka tawaaf to kar ley lekin Safa aur Marwa ki saee nahi karta, kya wo apni biwi se sohbat kar sakta hai. unhon-ne jawab diya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka) tashrif laey to aap ne Baitullah ka saat (7) chakkaron ke sath tawaaf kya aur maqaame-Ibraaheem ke peechhey 2 rakaat Namaz padhi. phir Safa aur Marwa ki saat (7) martaba saee ki aur tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi behtreen namoona hai."
1646,Safa aur Marwa ki saee se pahley biwi ke qareeb bhi na jaey.
1647,"maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, aap ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Makka tashrif laey to aap ne Baitullah ka tawaaf kya aur 2 rakaat Namaz padhi phir Safa aur Marwa ki saee ki. iske baad Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye aayat tilawat ki  لقد كان لكم في رسول الله أسوة حسنة '' tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi behtreen namoona hai.''"
1648,"aap log Safa aur Marwa ki saee ko bura samajhtey they? unhon-ne farmaya, haan ! kyonke ye ahade-jaahiliyat ka shiaar tha. yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farma di ''Safaa aur Marwa Allah Taala ki nishaniyan hain. to jo koi Baitullah ka Haj ya Umra karey is par unki saee karne mein koi gunah nahi hai.''"
1649,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee is tarah ki ke mushrekeen ko aap apni quwwat dikhla sakein. Humaidii ne ye izafa kya hai ke ham se Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya, unse Amr-bin-Dinar ne bayan kya, kaha ke maine Ata se suna aur unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se yahi hadis suni."
1650,main Makka aai to us waqt main haaiza thi. isliye Baitullah ka tawaaf na kar saki aur na Safa Marwa ki saee. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine uski shikayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ki to aap ne farmaya ke jis tarah doosrey haji kartey hain tum bhi isi tarah (arkaane-Haj) ada kar lo haan Baitullah ka tawaaf paak honey se pahley na karna.
1651,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke ashaab ne Haj ka ehram baandhaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Talha ke siwa aur kisi ke sath qurbani nahi thi, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yaman se aaey they aur unke sath bhi qurbani thi. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke (sab log apne Haj ke ehram ko) Umre ka kar lein. phir tawaaf aur saee ke baad baal tarashwa lein aur ehram khol daalein lekin wo log us hukm se mustashnaa hain jinke sath qurbani ho. is par sahaba ne kaha ke ham Mina mein is tarah jaeinge ke hamarey zakar (private part) se mani tapak rahi ho. ye baat jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko malum hui to aap ne farmaya, agar mujhey pahley malum hota to main qurbani ka janwar sath na laataa aur jab qurbani ka janwar sath na hota to main bhi (Umra aur Haj ke darmyaan) ehram khol daalta aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (is Haj mein) haaiza ho gaee thin. isliye unhon-ne Baitullah ke tawaaf ke siwa aur doosrey arkaane-Haj ada kiye. phir paak ho lin to tawaaf bhi kya. unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shikayat ki ke aap sab log to Haj aur Umra donon karke ja rahe hain lekin maine sirf Haj hi kya hai. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-Bakar ko hukm diya ke unhein taneem liye jayen (aur wahan se Umre ka ehram baandhein) is tarah Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Haj ke baad Umra kya."
1652,"ham apni kunwari ladkiyon ko bahar nikalney se roktey they. phir aik khatun aaein aur banii-khalaf ke mahal mein (jo Basra mein tha) thahriin. unhon-ne bayan kya ke unki behan (umme-Atiya (rz)) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik sahabi ke ghar mein thin. unke shauhar ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baara jihad kiye they aur meri behan chh jihaadon mein unke sath rahi thin. wo bayan karti thin ke ham (maidaane-jang mein) zakhmiyon ki marham-pattii karti thin aur mareezon ki teemaardaarii karti thi. meri behan ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke agar hamarey paas chadar na ho to kya koi harj hai agar ham eidgaah janey ke liye bahar na niklein? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, uski saheli ko apni chadar usey udha deni chahiye aur phir musalmanon ki dua aur nek kaamon mein shirkat karna chahiye phir jab umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) khud Basra aaein to maine unse bhi yahi puchha ya ye kaha ke hamne unse puchha unhon-ne bayan kya umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) jab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr kartin to kehtin mere bap aap par fidaa hun. haan to maine unse poochha, kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is tarah suna hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke haan, mere bap aap par fidaa hun. unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kunwari ladkiyan aur parde waaliyaan bhi bahar niklin ya ye farmaya ke parde wali ladkiyan aur haaiza auratein sab bahar niklin aur musalmanon ki dua aur khair ke kaamon mein shirkat karein. lekin haaiza auratein Namaz ki jagah se alag rahen. maine kaha aur haaiza bhi nikliin? unhon-ne farmaya ke kya haaiza aurat Arafaat aur falan-falan jagah nahi jati hain? (phir eidgaah hi janey mein kya harj hai)."
1653,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar aur Asr ki Namaz aathwein Zil-Hijja mein kahan padhi thi? agar aapko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yad hai to mujhey bataaiye. unhon-ne jawab diya ke Mina mein. maine puchha ke baarahviin taareekh ko Asr kahan padhi thi? farmaya ke Muhassab mein. phir unhon-ne farmaya ke jis tarah tumharey hukkaam kartey hain isi tarah tum bhi karo.
1654,main aathwein taareekh ko Mina gaya to wahan Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se mila. wo gadhi par Sawar ho kar ja rahe they. maine puchha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us din Zohar ki Namaz kahan padhi thi? unhon-ne farmaya dekho jahan tumharey Hakim log Namaz padhein wahin tum bhi padho.
1655,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Mina mein 2 rakaat padhein aur Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aisa kartey rahe aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi khilafat ke shuru dinon main (2) hi rakaat padhtey they.
1656,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Mina mein hamein 2 rakaat padhaaiin, hamara shumaar us waqt sabse zyada tha aur ham itney be-dar kisi waqt mein na they. (iske bawajud ham ko Namaz qasr padhaaii)."
1657,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Mina mein 2 rakaat Namaz padhi aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bhi 2 hi rakaat padhi aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bhi 2 hi rakaat, lekin phir unke baad tum mein ikhtilaf ho gaya to kash! un char rakaton ke badley mujh ko 2 rakaat hi naseeb hotiin jo ( Allah ke yahaan) qabool ho jaaein."
1658,"Arfa ke din logon ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rozey ke mutaalliq shak hua, isliye maine aapko peeney ke liye kuchh bheja jisey aap ne pi liya."
1659,"wo donon subah ko Mina se Arafaat ja rahe they. ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aap log aaj ke din kis tarah kartey they? Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaayaa: koi ham mein se labbaik pukarta hota, is par koi aetraz na karta aur koi takbeer kehtaa, is par koi inkar na karta (is hadis se malum hua ke haji ko ikhtiyar hai labbaik pukarta rahe ya takbeer kehta rahe)."
1660,"Haj ke ehkaam main Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke khilaf na kare. Salim ne kaha ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Arfa ke din suraj dhaltey hi tashrif laey mein bhi unke sath tha. aap ne Hajjaj ke khema ke paas buland awaz se pukara . Hajjaj bahar nikla iske badan mein aik Kusum mein rangi hui chadar thi. us ne puchha abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya baat hai? aap ne farmaya agar sunnat ke mutabiq amal chahtey ho to jaldi uth kar chal khadey ho jao. usne kaha kya usi waqt? Abdullah ne farmaya ke haan, usi waqt. Hajjaj ne kaha ke phir thodi si mohlat dijiye ke main apne sar par pani daal loon yani ghusl kar loon phir nikalta hun. iske baad Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) sawari se) utar gaey aur jab Hajjaj bahar aaya to mere aur walid ( ibne-Umar (ke darmyan chalney laga to maine kaha ke agar sunnat par amal ka irada hai to khutbe mein ikhtisar aur waquf ( Arafaat ( mein jaldi karna. is baat par wo Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf dekhney laga Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye sach kehta hai."
1661,"unke yahan logon ka Arafaat ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rozey se mutaalliq kuchh ikhtilaf ho gaya, kuchh ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Arfa ke din) rozey se hain aur kuchh kehtey hain ke nahi, isliye unhon-ne aap ke paas doodh ka aik piyala bhejaa, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt oont par Sawar ho kar Arafaat mein waquf farma rahe they, aap ne wo doodh pi liya."
1662,"Hajjaj-bin-Yosuf jis saal Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se ladney ke liye Makka mein utra to us mauqe par us ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Arfa ke din waquf mein aap kya kartey they? is par Salim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) boley ke agar to sunnat par chalnaa chahta hai to Arfa ke din Namaz do-pahar dhaltey hi padh lenaa. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Salim ne sach kaha, sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat ke mutabiq Zohar aur Asr aik hi sath padhtey they. maine Salim se puchha ke kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi isi tarah kya tha? Salim ne farmaya aur kis ki sunnat par us mas'ale mein chaltey ho."
1663,"Haj ke kaamon main Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) kare. jab Arfa ka din aaya to Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aaey mein bhi aap ke sath tha, suraj dhal chuka tha, aap ne Hajjaj ke derey ke paas aa kar buland awaz se kaha Hajjaj kahan hai? Hajjaj bahar nikla to ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya chal jaldi kar waqt ho gaya. Hajjaj ne kaha abhi se? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke haan. Hajjaj bola ke phir thodi mohlat de dijiye, mein abhi ghusl karke aata hun. phir Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) (apni sawari se) utar gaey. Hajjaj bahar nikla aur mere aur mere walid (ibne-Umar) ke beech mein chalney laga, maine usse kaha ke aaj agar sunnat par amal ki khahish hai to khutba mukhtasar padh aur waquf mein jaldi kar. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Salim sach kehta hai."
1664,"mera aik oont kho gaya tha to main Arafaat mein usko talash karne gaya, ye din Arafaat ka tha, maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Arafaat ke maidan mein khadey hain. meri zaban se nikla qism Allah ki ! ye to Quraish hain phir ye yahan kyon hain."
1665,"teiswin ke siwa Baqiiya sab log jahiliyat mein nangey ho kar tawaaf kartey they, teiswin Quraish aur uski aal-aulaad ko kehtey they, (aur bani kinaana wghaira, jaisey khuza'aa) logon ko (Allah ke waastey) kapdey diya kartey they. (Quraish) ke mard doosrey mardon ko taake unhein pahan kar tawaaf kar sakein aur (Quraish ki) auratein dusri aurton ko taake wo unhein pahan kar tawaaf kar sakein, aur jinko Quraish kapda nahi detey wo Baitullah ka tawaaf nangey ho kar kartey. doosrey sab log to Arafaat se wapas hotey lekin Quraish Muzdalfa hi se (jo haram mein tha) wapas ho jatey. Hisham-bin-Urwa ne kaha ke mere bap Urwa-bin-Zubair ne mujhey Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di ke ye aayat Quraish ke barey mein nazil hui ke ''phir tum bhi) Quraish ( wahin se wapas aao jahan se aur log wapas aatey hain'' (yani Arafaat se, sura al-Baqara) unhon-ne bayan kya ke Quraish Muzdalfa hi se lot aatey they isliye unhein bhi Arafaat se lotney ka hukm hua."
1666,"Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se kisi ne puchha (mein bhi wahin maujood tha) ke Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Arafaat se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wapas honey ki chaal kya thi? unhon-ne jawab diya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) paon utha kar chaltey they zara tez, lekin jab jagah patey (hujoom na hotaa) to tez chaltey they, Hisham ne kaha ke) عنق‏ ( tez chalnaa aur) nas ( ) عنق‏ ( se zyada tez chalney ko kehtey hain. ( فجوة (ke mana kushaada jagah , uski jama ( فجوات (aur ( فجاء ( hai jaisey zakat mufrad ( زكاء‏ ( uski jama aur sura ص (Swaad) mein (مناص) ka jo lafz aaya hai iske mana bhagna hai."
1667,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Arafaat se wapas huey they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( raah mein) aik ghaati ki taraf mudey aur wahan qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ki phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya to maine puchha ya Rasulullah ! kya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maghrib ki) Namaz padhengey ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Namaz aagey chal kar padhi jaeygi. (yani Arafaat se Muzdalfa aatey huey qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) wghaira ke liye raaste mein rukney mein koi harj nahi hai)."
1668,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Muzdalfa mein aa kar namaze-Maghrib aur isha mila kar aik sath padhtey , albatta aap us ghaati mein bhi mudte jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mudey they. wahan aap zarurat se farigh hotey phir wuzu kartey lekin Namaz na padhtey, Namaz aap Muzdalfa mein aa kar padhtey they."
1669,main Arafaat se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey betha hua tha. Muzdalfa ke qareeb baain taraf jo ghaati padtii hai jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne oont ko bithaya phir peshab kya aur tashrif laey to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wuzu ka pani dala. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne halka sa wuzu kya. maine kaha ya Rasulullah! aur namaaz? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ''namaaz tumharey aagey hai.'' (yani Muzdalfa mein padhi jaeygi) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sawar ho gaey jab Muzdalfa mein aaey to (maghrib aur isha ki) Namaz ( mila kar) padhi. phir Muzdalfa ki subah (yani dasween taareekh) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari ke peechhey Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) sawar huey.
1670,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) barabar labbaik kehtey rahe yahan tak ke jamara Aqba par pahunch gaey (aur wahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kankariyaan maarein).
1671,"Arfa ke din (maidaane-Arafaat se) wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aa rahe they Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne peechhey sakht shor (oont haankney ka (aur oonton ki maar-dhaad ki awaz suni to aap ne unki taraf apne kode se ishara kya aur farmaya ke logo! aahisatagi w waqaar apne uper lazim kar lo, (oonton ko) tez daudaanaa koi neki nahi hai. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) farmatey hain ke (sura al-Baqara mein) ( أوضعوا (ke mana resha dawaaniyaan karein, ( خلالكم (ka mana tumharey beech mein, usi se (sura Kahaf) mein aaya hai) وفجرنا خلالهما‏ ( yani unke beech mein."
1672,"maidaane-Arafaat se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rawaana ho kar ghaati mein utrey (jo Muzdalfa ke qareeb hai) wahan peshab kya, phir wuzu kya aur pura wuzu nahi kya (khoob pani nahi bahaya halka wuzu kya) maine Namaz ke mutaalliq kaha to farmaya ke Namaz aagey hai. ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Muzdalfa tashrif laey wahan phir wuzu kya aur poori tarah kya phir Namaz ki takbeer kahi gaee aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maghrib ki Namaz padhi phir har shakhs ne apne oont deron par bitha diye phir dobara Namaz isha ke liye takbeer kahi gaee aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un donon namazon ke darmyan koi ( sunnat ya nafl ( Namaz nahi padhi thi."
1673,"ham se Aadam-bin-abii-al-Ulaa ne bayan kya, kaha ham se ibne-abii-Zi'ib ne bayan kya, unse Zohri ne unse Saalim-bin-Abdullaah-bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Muzdalfa main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maghrib aur isha aik sath mila kar padhein thin har Namaz alag-alag takbeer ke sath na un donon ke darmyan koi nafl w sunnat padhi thi aur na unke ba'd."
1674,Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzdalfa mein aa kar maghrib aur isha ko aik sath mila kar padha tha.
1675,"Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Haj kya, aap ke sath taqriban isha ki azan ke waqt ham Muzdalfa mein bhi aaey, aap ne aik shakhs ko hukm diya usne azan aur takbeer kahi aur aap ne maghrib ki Namaz padhi, phir 2 rakaat ( sunnat (aur padhi aur Sham ka khana mangwa kar khaayaa. mera khayal hai (hadees ke rawi Zuhair ka (ke phir aap ne hukm diya aur us shakhs ne azan di aur takbeer kahi Amr (hadees ke raawii) ne kaha, main yahi samajhta hun ke shak Zuhair ( Amr ke Shekh ( ko tha, iske baad isha ki Namaz 2 rakaat padhi. jab subah sadiq hui to aap ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us Namaz ( fajr ( ko us maqam aur us din ke siwa aur kabhi us waqt ( tuloo fajr hotey hi) nahi padhtey they, Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bhi farmaya ke ye sirf 2 namazein (aaj ke din) apne maamooli waqt se hata di jati hain. jab log Muzdalfa aatey hain to maghrib ki Namaz (ishaa ke sath mila kar) padhi jati hai aur fajr ki Namaz tuloo fajr ke sath hii. unhon-ne farmaya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey dekha tha."
1676,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apne ghar ke kamzoron ko pahley hi bhej diya kartey they aur wo raat hi mein Muzdalfa mein mash'ar haram ke paas aa kar thahartey aur apni taqat ke mutabiq Allah ka zikr kartey they, phir imam ke thaharney aur lotney se pahley hi ( Mina ( aa jatey they, kuchh to Mina fajr ki Namaz ke waqt pahunchtey aur kuchh iske ba'd, jab Mina pahunchtey to kankariyaan maartey aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un sab logon ke liye ye ijazat di hai."
1677,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey Muzdalfa se raat hi mein Mina rawaana kar diya tha.
1678,main un logon mein tha jinhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ghar ke kamzor logon ke sath Muzdalfa ki raat hi mein Mina bhej diya tha.
1679,"wo raat hi mein Muzdalfa pahunch gain aur khadi ho kar Namaz padhney lagiin, kuchh der tak Namaz padhney ke baad puchha betey! kya chaand doob gayaa? maine kaha ke nahi, isliye wo dobara Namaz padhney lagiin kuchh der baad phir puchha kya chaand doob gayaa? maine kaha haan, unhon-ne kaha ke ab aagey chalo (Minaa ko) chunanche ham unke sath aagey chaley, wo (Minaa mein) rami jamara karne ke baad phir wapas aa gain aur subah ki Namaz apne derey par padhi maine kaha janab ! ye kya baat hui ke ham ne andherey hi mein Namaz padh li. unhon-ne kaha betey! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton ko uski ijazat di hai."
1680,Ummul-Momenin Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Muzdalfa ki raat aam logon se pahley rawaana honey ki ijazat chahi aap (Raziallahu anhu) bhari bharkam badan ki aurat thin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein uski ijazat de di.
1681,"jab ham ne Muzdalfa mein qiyam kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ko logon ke izdahaam se pahley rawaana honey ki ijazat de di thi, wo bhari bharkam badan ki khatun thin, isliye aap ne ijazat de di chunanche wo izdahaam se pahley rawaana ho gaiin. lekin ham wahin thahrey rahe aur subah ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath gaey agar main bhi Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ki tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat leti to mujh ko tamam khushi ki chizon mein ye bahut hi pasand hota."
1682,"2 namazon ke siwa maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aur koi Namaz baghair waqt nahi padhtey dekha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maghrib aur isha aik sath padhein aur fajr ki Namaz bhi us din (Muzdalfa mein) mamool (routine) ke waqt se pahley ada ki."
1683,"ham Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Makka ki taraf nikley (Haj shuru kya) phir jab ham Muzdalfa aaey to aap ne 2 namazein (is tarah aik saath) padhein ke har Namaz aik alag azan aur aik alag iqamat ke sath thi aur raat ka khana donon ke darmyan mein khaayaa, phir tuloo subah ke sath hi aap ne namaze-Fajr padhi, koi kehta tha ke abhi subah sadiq nahi hui aur kuchh log keh rahe they ke ho gaee. iske baad Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ye donon namazein us maqam se hata di gain hain, yani maghrib aur ishaa, Muzdalfa mein us waqt dakhil hon ke andhera ho jaey aur fajr ki Namaz us waqt. phir Abdullah ujaaley tak wahin Muzdalfa mein thahrey rahe aur kaha ke agar ameerul-momineen Usman (Raziallahu anhu) us waqt chalein to ye sunnat ke mutabiq hoga. ( hadis ke rawi Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed ne kaha) mein nahi keh sakta ke ye alfaz unki zaban se pahley nikley ya Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki rawaangii pahley shuru hui, aap dasween taareekh tak jamara Aqba ki rami tak barabar labbaik pukaartey rahe."
1684,"jab umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muzdalfa mein fajr ki Namaz padhi to main bhi maujood tha, Namaz ke baad aap thahrey aur farmaya ke mushrekeen (jaahiliyat mein yahan se) suraj nikalney se pahley nahi jatey they kehtey they aey Sabeer! to chamak jaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mushrikon ki mukhalifat ki aur suraj nikalney se pahley wahan se rawaana ho gaey."
1685,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Muzdalfa se laut'tey waqt) Fazal (bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ko apne peechhey sawar karaya tha. Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rami jamara tak barabar labbaik pukaartey rahe.
1686,"Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Arafaat se Muzdalfa tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari par aap ke peechhey baithey huey they, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzdalfa se Mina jatey waqt Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne peechhey bitha liya tha. unhon-ne kaha ke un donon hazraat ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jamara Aqba ki rami tak musalsal labbaik kehtey rahe."
1687,"Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Arafaat se Muzdalfa tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari par aap ke peechhey baithey huey they, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzdalfa se Mina jatey waqt Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne peechhey bitha liya tha. unhon-ne kaha ke un donon hazraat ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jamara Aqba ki rami tak musalsal labbaik kehtey rahe."
1688,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se tamatto ke barey mein puchha to aap ne mujhey iske karne ka hukm diya, phir maine qurbani ke mutaalliq puchha to aap ne farmaya ke tamatto mein aik oont, ya aik gaaey ya aik bakri (ki qurbani wajib hai) ya kisi qurbani (oont, ya gaaey bheins ki) mein Sharik ho jaey, abu-Jamra ne kaha ke kuchh log tamatto ko na-pasandida qarar detey they. phir main soyaa to maine khuwab mein dekha ke aik shakhs pukar raha hai ye Haj mabroor hai aur ye maqbool tamatto hai. ab main Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unse khuwab ka zikr kya to unhon-ne farmaya : Allahu-akbar ! ye to abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat hai. kaha ke Wahab bin Jarir aur ghandar ne Shoba ke hawale se yun naql kya hai (عمرة متقبلة ، Mina وحج مبرور) (is mein Umre ka zikr pahley hai yani ye Umra maqbool aur Haj mabroor hai)."
1689,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko qurbani ka janwar ley jatey dekha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is par Sawar ho jaa. us shakhs ne kaha ke ye to qurbani ka janwar hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is par Sawar ho jaa. usne kaha ke ye to qurbani ka janwar hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya afsos ! sawar bhi ho jao ( ويلك (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) dusri ya teesri martaba farmaya,"
1690,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko dekha ke qurbani ka janwar liye ja raha hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is par Sawar ho ja usne kaha ke ye to qurbani ka janwar hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Sawar ho ja usne phir arz kya ke ye to qurbani ka janwar hai, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri martaba phir farmaya ke Sawar ho jaa."
1691,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada mein tamatto kya yani Umra karke phir Haj kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zul-Hulaifa se apne sath qurbani ley gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahley Umra ke liye ehram baandhaa, phir Haj ke liye labbaik pukara . logon ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tamatto kya yani Umra karke Haj kya, lekin bahut se log apne sath qurbani ka janwar le gaey they aur bahut se nahi le gaey they. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka tashrif laey to logon se kaha ke jo shakhs qurbani sath laya ho uske liye Haj pura honey tak koi bhi aisi cheez halal nahi ho sakti jisey usne apne uper (ehraam ki wjah se) haram kar liya hai lekin jinke sath qurbani nahi hai to wo Baitullah ka tawaaf kar lein aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee karke baal tarashwa lein aur halal ho jaaein, phir Haj ke liye (naye sire se aathwiin Zil-Hijja ko ehram baandhein) aisa shakhs agar qurbani na paaey to teen din ke rozey Haj hi ke dinon main aur saat (7) din ke rozey ghar wapas aa kar rakhey. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka pahunchey to sabse pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tawaaf kya phir hajre-Aswad ko bosa diya, teen chakkaron mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ramal kya aur baqi char mein maamooli raftaar se chaley, phir Baitullah ka tawaaf pura karke maqaame-Ibraaheem ke paas 2 rakaat Namaz padhi salam pher kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Safa pahaadii ki taraf aaey aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee bhi saat (7) chakkaron mein poori ki. jin chizon ko (ehraam ki wjah se apne par) haram kar liya tha unse us waqt tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) halal nahi huey jab tak Haj bhi pura na kar liya aur yaumun-Nahar (dasween zil-hijja) mein qurbani ka janwar bhi zabah na kar liya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka waapas) aaey aur Baitullah ka jab tawaafe-ifaaza kar liya to har wo cheez aap ke liye halal ho gaee jo ehram ki wjah se haram thi jo log apne sath qurbani ka janwar lekar gaey they unhon-ne bhi isi tarah kya jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha."
1692,"aur logon ne bhi aap ke sath Haj aur Umra aik sath kya tha, bilkul isi tarah jaisey mujhey Salim ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khabar di thi."
1693,"mera khayal hai ke (bd-amnii ki wjah se) aapko Baitullah tak pahunchne se rok diya jaeyga unhon-ne farmaya ke phir main bhi wahi kaam karunga jo (aisey mauqe par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha Allah Taala ne farmaya hai ke ''tumhaarey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi behtreen namoona hai'' mein ab tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine apne uper Umra wajib kar liya hai, chunanche aap ne Umre ka ehram baandhaa, unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir aap nikley aur jab beda pahunchey to Haj aur Umra donon ka ehram baandh liya aur farmaya ke Haj aur Umra donon to aik hi hain iske baad qudaid pahunch kar qurbani ka janwar khareeda phir Makka aa kar donon ke liye tawaaf kya aur darmyan mein nahi balke donon se aik hi sath halal huey."
1694,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina se taqriban apne aik hazaar sathiyon ke sath (Haj ke liye nikley) jab zul-Hulaifa pahunchey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ka janwar ko haar pahnaayaa aur ashaar kya phir Umre ka ehram baandhaa.
1695,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina se taqriban apne aik hazaar sathiyon ke sath ( Haj ke liye nikley ( jab zul-Hulaifa pahunchey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ka janwar ko haar pahnaayaa aur ashaar kya phir Umre ka ehram baandhaa.
1696,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qurbani ke janwaron ke haar maine apne hath se khud batey they, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein haar pahnaayaa, ashaar kya, unko Makka ki taraf rawaana kya phir bhi aap ke liye jo cheezein halal thin wo ( ehram se pahley sirf qurbani ka janwar se) haram nahi huin."
1697,"ya Rasulullah ! aur log to halal ho gaey lekin aap halal nahi huey, uski kya wjah hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine apne sar ke baalon ko jama liya hai aur apni qurbani ka janwar ko haar pehna diya hai, isliye jab tak Haj se bhi halal na ho jaun main (darmyaan mein) halal nahi ho sakta, (gond laga kar sar ke baalon ka jama lena usko talbeed kehtey hain)."
1698,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina se qurbani ka janwar sath lekar chaltey they aur main unke haar bata karti thi phir bhi aap (ehraam baandhney se pahley) un chizon se parhez nahi kartey they jin se aik ehram wala parhez karta hai.
1699,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qurbani ka janwar ke haar khud batey they, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ashaar kya aur haar pahnaayaa, ya maine haar pahnaayaa, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ke liye unhein bhej diya aur khud Madina mein thahar gaey lekin koi bhi aisi cheez Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye haram nahi hui jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye halal thi."
1700,"jisne qurbani ka janwar bhej diya is par wo tamam cheezein haram ho jati hain jo aik haji par haram hoti hain yahan tak ke uski qurbani ka janwar ki qurbani kar di jaey, Umra ne kaha ke is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo kuchh kaha masla is tarah nahi hai, maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qurbani ke janwaron ke haar apne hathon se khud batey hain, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hathon se un janwaron ko haar pahnaayaa aur mere walid mohtaram (abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ke sath unhein bhej diya lekin iske bawajud Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi bhi aisi cheez ko apne uper haram nahi kya jo Allah ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye halal ki thi, aur qurbani ke janwar ki qurbani bhi kar di gaee."
1701,aik martaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ke liye ( Baitullah ( bakriyan bheji thin.
1702,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qurbani ke janwaron ke haar khud bata karti thi, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bakri ko bhi haar pahnaayaa tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud apne ghar us haal mein muqeem they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) halal they."
1703,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bakriyon ke haar khud bata karti thi, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein (Baitullaah ke liye) bhej detey aur khud halal hi honey ki haalat main apne ghar thahar rehtey."
1704,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qurbani ke liye khud haar batey hain. unki murad ehram se pahley ke qalaadon se thi.
1705,mere paas jo oon thi unke haar maine qurbani ke janwaron ke liye khud batey they.
1706,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ko dekha ke wo qurbani ka oont liye ja raha hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is par Sawar ho jaa, usne kaha ke ye to qurbani ka hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke Sawar ho jaa. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir maine dekha ke wo is par Sawar hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chal raha hai aur jootey (ka haar (us oont ke gardan mein hai. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Muhammad-bin-Bashaar ne ki hai. ham se Usman bin umr ne bayan kya, ham ko Ali bin-Mubarak ne khabar di, unhein Yahya ne unhein Ikrima ne aur unhein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (misl pichhli hadis ki tarah) ."
1707,mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un qurbani ke janwaron ke jhool aur unke chamdey ko sadqa karne ka hukm diya tha jinki qurbani maine kar di thi.
1708,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke daure-khilaafat mein hajjal-Harooriya ke saal Haj ka irada kya to unse kaha gaya ke logon mein aapasii qatl w khoon honey wala hai aur ham ko khatrah iska hai ke aapko ( fasaadii log Haj se) rok dein, aap ne jawab mein ye aayat sunai ke '' tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi behtreen namoona hai.'' us waqt main bhi wahi kaam karunga jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha. main tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine apne uper Umra wajib kar liya hai, phir jab aap beda ke oopri hisse tak pahunchey to farmaya ke Haj aur Umra to aik hi hai main tumhen gawah banata hun ke Umra ke sath maine Haj ko bhi jama kar liya hai, phir aap ne aik qurbani ka janwar bhi sath ley liya jisey haar pahnaayaa gaya tha. aap ne usey khareed liya yahan tak ke aap Makka aaey to Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa w Marwa ki saee ki, us se zyada aur kuchh nahi kya jo cheezein (ehraam ki wjah se un par) haram thin unmein se kisi se qurbani ke din tak wo halal nahi huey, phir sar mundwaayaa aur qurbani ki wjah ye samajhtey they ke apna pahlaa tawaaf karke unhon-ne Haj aur Umra donon ka tawaaf pura kar liya hai phir aap ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi isi tarah kya tha."
1709,"maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, unhon-ne batlaya ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (Haj ke liye) nikley to Zi-Qada mein se panch din baqi rahe they ham sirf Haj ka irada lekar nikley they, jab ham Makka ke qareeb pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke jin logon ke sath qurbani na ho wo jab tawaaf kar lein aur Safa w Marwa ki saee bhi kar lein to halal ho jaaeinge, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke qurbani ke din hamarey ghar gaaey ka gosht laya gaya to maine kaha ke ye kya hai? ( laney waley ne batlaya (ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ki taraf se ye qurbani ki hai, Yahya ne kaha ke maine Umra ki ye hadis Qasim se bayan ki unhon-ne kaha Umra ne ye hadis theek theek bayan ki hai."
1710,"Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) nehar karne ki jagah nehar kartey they, unke bete Ubaidullah ne bataya ke murad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nehar karne ki jagah se thi."
1711,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apni qurbani ke janwaron ko Muzdalfa se aakhir raat mein Mina bhijwa detey, ye qurbaniyan jin mein haji log neez ghulam aur aazad donon tarah ke log hotey, us maqam mein ley jatey jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nehar kya kartey they."
1712,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saat (7) oont khadey karke apne hath se nehar kiye aur Madina mein 2 chitkabrey seeng daar mendhon ki qurbani ki.
1713,"maine dekha ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aik shakhs ke paas aaey jo apna oont bitha kar nehar kar raha tha, Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke usey khada kar aur baandh de, phir nehar karke yahi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat hai. Shoba ne Yunus se bayan kya ke mujhey zyada ne khabar di."
1714,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz Madina mein char rakaat padhi aur Asr ki zul-Hulaifa mein 2 rak'aat. raat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahin guzaarii, phir jab subah hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni ontni par Sawar ho kar tahleel w tasbeeh karne lagey. jab beda pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon ( Haj w Umra (ke liye aik sath talbiya kaha, jab Makka pahunchey (aur Umra ada kar liya ( to sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke halal ho jaaein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud apne hath se saat (7) oont khadey karke nehar kiye aur Madina mein 2 chitkabrey seengon waley mendhey zabah kiye."
1715,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz Madina mein char rakaat aur Asr ki zul-Hulaifa mein 2 rakaat padhi thin. Ayub ne aik shakhs ke waaste se b-riwayat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kaha phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahin raat guzari . subah hui to fajr ki Namaz padhi aur apni ontni par Sawar ho gaey, phir jab maqam beda pahunchey to Umra aur Haj donon ka naam lekar labbaik pukara ."
1716,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ( qurbani ke oonton ki dekh bhaal ke liye) bhejaa. isliye maine unki dekh bhaal ki, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya to maine unke gosht taqseem kiye, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya to maine unke jhool aur chamdey bhi taqseem kar diye. Sufiyan ne kaha ke mujh se Abdul-Karim ne bayan kya, unse Mujahid ne, unse Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-Lailaa ne aur unse Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya tha ke main qurbani ke oonton ki dekh-bhaal karun aur unmein se koi cheez qasaaii ki mazdoorii mein na dun."
1717,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qurbani ke oonton ki nigrani karein aur ye ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qurbani ke janwaron ki har cheez gosht chamdey aur jhol khairat kar dein aur qasaaii ki mazdoorii usmein se na dein.
1718,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par) so oont qurbaan kiye, maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm ke mutabiq unke gosht baant diye, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke jhool bhi taqseem karne ka hukm diya aur maine unhein bhi taqseem kya, phir chamdey ke liye hukm diya aur maine unhein bhi baant diya."
1719,"ham apni qurbani ka gosht Mina ke baad teen din se zyada nahi khaatey they, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ijazat de di aur farmaya ke khaao bhi aur khane-pine ka saman ke taur par sath bhi ley jao, chunanche ham ne khaya aur sath bhi laey. ibne-Juraij ne kaha ke maine Ata se puchha kya Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bhi kaha tha ke yahan tak ke ham Madina pahunch gaey, unhon-ne kaha nahi aisa nahi farmaya,"
1720,"ham Madina se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley to Zi-Qada ke panch din baqi reh gaey they, hamara irada sirf Haj hi ka tha, phir jab Makka ke qareeb pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jinke sath qurbani ka janwar na ho wo Baitullah ka tawaaf karke halal ho jaaein. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke phir hamarey paas Baaqar eid ke din gaaey ka gosht laya gaya to maine puchha ke ye kya hai? us waqt malum hua ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ki taraf se qurbani ki hai. Yahya-bin-Saeed ne kaha ke maine us hadis ka Qasim-bin-Muhammad se zikr kya to unhon-ne kaha ke Umra ne tum se theek theek hadis bayan kar di hai. (har 2 hadison se maqsad baab zahir hai) ke qurbani ka gosht khaney aur bataur khane-pine ka saman rakhney ki aam ijazat hai, khud Quran Majeed main ( فكلوا منها (ka seegha maujood hai ke usey غرباء miskinon ko bhi taqseem karo aur khud bhi khaao."
1721,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us shakhs ke barey mein puchha gaya jo qurbani ka janwar zabah karne se pahley hi sar mundwaa ley, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya koi qabahat nahi, koi qabahat nahi. (tarjama aur baab mein muwafiqat zahir hai)."
1722,"aik aadmi ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! rami se pahley maine tawaaf ziyaarat kar liya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi harj nahi, phir usne kaha aur ya Rasulullah! qurbani karne se pahley maine sar mundwaa liya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya koi harj nahi, phir usne kaha aur qurbani ko rami se bhi pahley kar liya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir bhi yahi farmaya ke koi harj nahi. aur abdur-Raheem razi ne ibne-Khushaim se bayan kya, kaha ke Ata ne khabar di aur unhein Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Qasim bin Yahya ne kaha ke mujh se ibne-Khushaim ne bayan kya, unse ata ne, unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. Affaan-bin-Muslim sighaar ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ke Wuhaib bin Khalid se riwayat hai ke ibne-Khaseem ne bayan kya, unse Saeed-bin-Jubair ne, unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. aur Hammad ne Qais-bin-Sad aur Ibaad-bin-Mansoor se bayan kya, unse Ata ne aur unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya."
1723,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik aadmi ne masla puchha ke Sham honey ke baad maine rami ki hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi harj nahi. sawal karnewaale ne kaha ke qurbani karne se pahley maine sar mundaa liya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi harj nahi."
1724,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap Batha mein they. (jo Makka ke qareeb aik jagah hai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya tu ney Haj ki niyat ki hai? maine kaha ke haan, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tu ney ehram kis cheez ka baandha hai maine kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ehram ki tarah baandha hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tu ney achchha kya ab jaa. chunanche (Makka pahunch kar) maine Baitullah ka tawaaf kya aur Safa w Marwa ki saee ki, phir main banu-Qais ki aik khatun ke paas aaya aur unhon-ne mere sar ki juein nikaalii. iske baad maine Haj ki labbaik pukaarii. iske baad main umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke daure-khilaafat tak usi ka fatwa deta raha phir jab maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se iska zikr kya to aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke hamein kitabullah par bhi amal karna chahiye aur is mein pura karne ka hukm hai, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat par bhi amal karna chahiye aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qurbani se pahley halal nahi huey they."
1725,"Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya wjah hui ke aur log to Umra karke halal ho gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umra kar liya aur halal na huey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine apne sar ke baal jama liye they aur qurbani ke galley mein haar pehna kar main (apne saath) laya hon, isliye jab tak main nehar na kar loonga main ehram nahi kholunga."
1726,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par apna sar mundaayaa tha.
1727,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki aey Allah ! sar mundwaaney walon par raham farma ! sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aur katarwaaney walon par? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ab bhi dua ki aey Allah sar mundwaaney walon par raham farma ! sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne phir kaha aur katarwaaney walon par? ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur katarwaaney walon par bhi, Leis ne kaha ke mujh se Naafe ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Allah ne sar mundwaaney walon par raham kya aik ya 2 martaba , unhon-ne bayan kya ke Ubaidullah ne kaha ke mujh se Naafe ne bayan kya ke chothi martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke katarwaaney walon par bhii."
1728,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai aey Allah ! sar mundwaaney walon ki maghfirat farma ! sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya aur katarwaaney walon ke liye bhi) yahi dua farmaiye) lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us martaba bhi yahi farmaya aey Allah ! sar mundwaaney walon ki maghfirat kar. phir sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya aur katarwaaney walon ki bhi ! teesri martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur katarwaaney walon ki bhi maghfirat farmaa.
1729,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bahut se ashaab ne sar mundwaayaa tha lekin kuchh ne katarwaayaa bhi tha.
1730,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baal qainchi se kaatey they.
1731,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ashaab ko ye hukm diya ke Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa w Marwa ki saee karne ke baad ehram khol dein phir sar mundwaa lein ya baal katarwaa lein.
1732,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne sirf aik tawaafe-ziyaara kya phir sawerey se Mina ko aaey, unki murad dasween taareekh se thi, Abdur-Razzaq ne us hadis ka rafa' (hadees ki sanad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak) bhi kya hai. unhein Ubaidullah ne khabar di."
1733,"ham ne jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj kya to dasween taareekh ko tawaafe-ziyaara kya lekin Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) haaiza ho gain phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse wahi chaha jo shauhar apni biwi se chahta hai, to maine kaha ya Rasulullah ! wo haaiza hain, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke usne to hamein rok diya phir jab logon ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! unhon-ne dasween taareekh ko tawaafe-ziyaara kar liya tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir chaley chalo. Qaasim, Urwa aur Aswad se b-waaste Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) riwayat hai ke Ummul-Momenin Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne dasween taareekh ko tawaafe-ziyaara kya tha."
1734,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se qurbani karne, sar mundaaney, rami jimaar karne aur unse aagey peechhey karne ke barey mein malum kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi harj nahi."
1735,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yaumun-nahar mein Mina mein masayel poochhey jatey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey jatey ke koi harj nahi, aik shakhs ne puchha tha ke maine qurbani karne se pahley sar mundaa liya hai to aap ne iske jawab mein bhi yahi farmaya ke jao qurbani kar lo koi harj nahi aur us ne ye bhi puchha ke maine kankariyaan Sham honey ke baad hi mar li hain, to bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi harj nahi."
1736,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par (apni sawari ( par baithey huey they aur log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se masayel malum kiye ja rahe they. aik shakhs ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! mujh ko malum na tha aur maine qurbani karne se pahley hi sar mundaa liya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ab qurbani kar lo koi harj nahi, doosra shakhs aaya aur bola : ya Rasulullah ! mujhey khayal na raha aur rami jimaar se pahley hi maine qurbani kar di, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ab rami kar lo koi harj nahi, us din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jis cheez ke aagey peechhey karne ke mutaalliq sawal hua Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi farmaya ab kar lo koi harj nahi."
1737,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dasween taareekh ko Mina mein khutba de rahe they, to wo wahan maujood they. aik shakhs ne us waqt khadey ho kar puchha ke main us khayal mein tha ke falan kaam falan se pahley hai phir doosra khada hua aur kaha ke mera khayal tha ke falan kaam falan se pahley hai, chunanche maine qurbani se pahley sar mundaa liya, rami jimaar se pahley qurbani kar li, aur mujhey usmein shak hua. to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ab kar lo. un sab mein koi harj nahi. isi tarah ke doosrey sawalat bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kiye gaey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un sab ke jawab mein yahi farmaya ke koi harj nahi ab kar lo."
1738,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sawari par Sawar ho kar thahrey rahe phir poori hadis bayan ki. uski mutabiat (pairavi) Mamar ne Zohri se riwayat karke ki hai.
1739,"dasween taareekh ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Mina mein khutba diya, khutbe mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha logo! aaj kon sa din hai? log boley ye hurmat ka din hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir puchha aur ye Shahar kon sa hai? logon ne kaha ye hurmat ka Shahar hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ye mahina kon sa hai? logon ne kaha ye hurmat ka mahina hai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya bas tumhara khoon tumharey maal aur tumhari izzat aik doosrey par isi tarah haram hai jaisey us din ki hurmat, us Shahar aur us mahina ki hurmat hai, us kalime ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kai baar dohraya aur phir aasman ki taraf sar utha kar kaha aey Allah ! kya maine (teraa paighaam) pahuncha diya aey Allah ! kya maine pahuncha diya. Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ye wasiiyat apni tamam ummat ke liye hai, lihaza hazir (aur jaanney waale) ghayab (aur na-waqif logon ko Allah ka paighaam) pahuncha dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya dekho mere baad aik doosrey ki gardan mar kar kaafir na bin jaanaa."
1740,maidaane-Arafaat main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khutba maine khud suna tha. uski mutabiat (pairavi) ibne-Uena ne Amr se ki hai.
1741,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dasween taareekh ko Mina mein khutba sunaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha logo ! malum hai aaj ye kon sa din hai? ham ne kaha Allah aur uska rasool zyada jantey hain, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par khamosh ho gaey aur ham ne samjha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us din ka koi aur naam rakhengey lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya ye qurbani ka din nahi. ham boley haan zaroor hai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ye mahina kon sa hai? ham ne kaha Allah aur uske rasool zyada jantey liye. aap us martaba bhi khamosh ho gaey aur hamein khayal hua ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us maheene ka naam kuchh aur rakhengey, lekin aap ne farmaya kya ye Zil-Hijja ka mahina nahi hai? ham boley kyon nahi, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ye Shahar kon sa hai? ham ne kaha Allah aur uske rasool behtar jantey hain, us martaba bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is tarah khamosh ho gaey ke ham ne samjha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iska koi aur naam rakhengey , lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye hurmat ka Shahar nahi hai? ham ne kaha kyon nahi zaroor hai, iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya bas tumhara khoon aur tumharey maal tum par isi tarah haram hain jaisey us din ki hurmat us maheene aur us Shahar mein hai, yahan tak ke tum apne rab se ja milo. kaho kya maine tum ko Allah ka paigham pahuncha diya? logon ne kaha ke haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey Allaah! to gawah rehna aur haan! yahan maujood ghayab ko pahuncha dein kyonke bahut se log jin tak ye paigham pahunchega sunney walon se zyada (paighaam ko) yad rakhney waley Sabit hongey aur mere baad kaafir na bin jana ke eik-doosrey ki) nahaq ( gardanein maarney lago."
1742,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Mina mein farmaya ke tum ko malum hai ! aaj kon sa din hai? logon ne kaha ke Allah aur uske rasool zyada jantey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye hurmat ka din hai aur ye bhi tum ko malum hai ke ye kon sa Shahar hai? logon ne kaha Allah aur uske rasool zyada jantey hain, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye hurmat ka Shahar hai aur tum ko ye bhi malum hai ke ye kon sa mahina hai, logon ne kaha Allah aur uske rasool zyada jantey hain, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye hurmat ka mahina hai phir farmaya ke Allah Taala ne tumhara khoon ! tumhara maal aur izzat aik doosrey par) nahaq ( is tarah haram kar di hain jaisey us din ki hurmat us mahina aur us Shahar mein hai. Hishaam-bin-Ghaaz ne kaha ke mujhey Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hijjatul-wada mein dasween taareekh ko jamaraat ke darmyan khadey huey they aur farmaya tha ke dekho! ye (Yaumun-Nahar) Haje-akbar ka din hai, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye farmaney lagey ke aey Allaah! gawah rehna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us mauqe par chunkey logon ko rukhsat kya tha. (aap samajh gaey ke wafat ka zamana aan pahunchaa) jab se log us Haj ko Hijjatul-wada kehney lagey."
1743,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ijazat di.
1744,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ijazat di.
1745,Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Mina ki raaton main ( haajiyon ( ko pani pilaaney ke liye Makka mein rehney ki ijazat chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko ijazat de di. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Muhammad-bin-Abdullah ke sath abu-Usama Aqba-bin-Khalid aur abu-Zamra ne ki hai.
1746,"jab tumhara imam (kankriyaan) maarey to tum bhi maaro, lekin dobara maine unse yahi masla puchha to unhon-ne farmaya ke ham intizar kartey rahtey aur jab suraj dhal jata to kankariyaan maartey."
1747,"Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne wadi ke nasheb (batan waadii) mein khadey ho kar kankari maari to maine kaha, aey abu-Abdur-Rehmaan! kuchh log to wadi ke oopri ilaqe se kankariyaan maartey hain, iska jawab unhon-ne ye diya ke us zaat ki qasam! jiske siwa koi maabood nahi yahi ( batan waadii) unke khadey honey ki jagah hai) rami kartey waqt) jin par sura al-Baqara nazil hui thi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . Abdullah-bin Waleed ne bayan kya ke unse Sufiyan Sory ne aur unse Aamash ne yahi hadis bayan ki."
1748,"Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) jamara kubraa ke paas pahunchey to Kaba ko apne baain taraf kya aur Mina ko daain taraf, phir saat (7) kankariyon se rami ki aur farmaya ke jin par sura al-Baqara nazil hui thi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhon-ne bhi isi tarah rami ki thi. (yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ."
1749,unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Haj kya unhon-ne dekha jamara Aqba ki saat (7) kankariyon ke sath rami ke waqt aap ne Baitullah ko to apni baain taraf aur mani ko daain taraf kar liya phir farmaya ke yahi unka bhi maqam tha jin par sura al-Baqara nazil hui thi yani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) .
1750,"maine Hajjaj se suna, wo member par Suraton ka yun naam ley raha tha wo sura jis mein Baqra (gaaey) ka zikr aaya hai, wo sura jis mein aale-Imraan ka zikr aaya hai, wo sura jis mein Nisa ( aurton (ka zikr aaya hai, Aamash ne kaha maine iska zikr Ibrahim Nakhai (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se kya to unhon-ne farmaya ke mujh se Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed ne bayan kya ke jab Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne jamara Aqba ki rami ki to wo unke sath they, us waqt wo wadi ke nasheb (nichle hisse) mein utar gaey aur jab darakht ke (jo us waqt wahan par tha) barabar nichey iske samney ho kar saat (7) kankariyon se rami ki har kankari ke sath Allahu-akbar kehtey jatey they. phir farmaya qism hai uski ke jis zaat ke siwa koi maabood nahi yahin wo zaat bhi khadi hui thi jis par sura al-Baqara nazil hui."
1751,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) pahley jamara ki rami saat (7) kankariyon ke sath kartey aur har kankari par) Allahu-akbar ( kehtey they, phir aagey badhtey aur aik narm hamwaar zameen par pahunch kar qibla rukh khadey ho jatey isi tarah der tak khadey donon hath utha kar dua kartey, phir jamara Wustaa ki rami kartey, phir baain taraf badhtey aur aik hamwaar zameen par qibla rukh ho kar khadey ho jatey, yahan bhi der tak khadey khadey donon hath utha kar duaein kartey rahtey , iske baad waley nasheb se jamarae-Aqba ki rami kartey iske baad aap khadey na hotey balke wapas chaley aatey aur farmatey ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey dekha tha."
1752,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) pahley jamara ki rami saat (7) kankariyon ke sath kartey aur har kankari par) Allahu-akbar ( kehtey they, iske baad aagey badhtey aur aik narm hamwaar zameen par qibla rukh khadey ho jatey, duaein kartey rahtey aur donon hathon ko uthatey phir jamara wustaa ki rami mein bhi isi tarah kartey aur baain taraf aagey badh kar aik narm zameen par qibla rukh khadey ho jatey, bahut der tak isi tarah khadey ho kar duaein kartey rahtey , phir jamara Aqba ki rami batan wadi se kartey lekin wahan thahartey nahi they, aap farmatey they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey dekha hai."
1753,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab us jamara ki rami kartey jo Mina ki masjid ke nazdeek hai to saat (7) kankariyon se rami kartey aur har kankari ke sath takbeer ( Allahu-akbar ( kehtey, phir aagey badhtey aur qibla rukh khadey ho kar donon hath utha kar duaein kartey they, yahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut der tak khadey rahtey they phir jamara saaniya ( wustaa (ke paas aatey yahan bhi saat (7) kankariyon se rami kartey aur har kankari ke sath ( Allahu-akbar ( kehtey, phir baain taraf naley ke qareeb utar jatey aur wahan bhi qibla rukh khadey hotey aur hathon ko utha kar dua kartey rahtey, phir jamara Aqba ke paas aatey aur yahan bhi saat (7) kankariyon se rami kartey aur har kankari ke sath (Allaahu-akbar) kehtey, iske baad wapas ho jatey yahan aap dua ke liye thahartey nahi they. Zohri ne kaha ke maine Salim se suna wo bhi isi tarah apne walid (ibne-Umar (rz)) se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis bayan kartey they aur ye ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) khud bhi isi tarah kya kartey they."
1754,"maine khud apne hathon se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke, jab aap ne ehram baandhna chaha, khushbu lagai thi is tarah kholtey waqt bhi jab aap ne tawaafe-ziyaara se pahley ehram kholnaa chaha tha (aap ne hath phaila kar khushbu lagaaney ki kaifiyat bataaii)."
1755,logon ko iska hukm tha ke unka aakhiri waqt Baitullah ke sath ho (yani tawaaf wadaa' karein) albatta haaiza se ye maaf ho gaya tha.
1756,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuhar, Asr, maghrib aur isha padhi, phir thodi der Muhassab mein so rahe, iske baad Sawar ho kar Baitullah tashrif le gaey aur wahan tawaafe-ziyaara Amr-bin-Haris ke sath kya, is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Leis ne ki hai, unse Khalid ne bayan kya, unse Saeed ne, unse Qatada ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kya hai."
1757,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Safiya-bint-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par) haaiza ho gain to maine iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir to ye hamein rokengii, logon ne kaha ke unhon-ne tawaafe-ifaaza kar liya hai, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir koi fikr nahi."
1758,"Madina ke logon ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aik aurat ke mutaalliq puchha ke jo tawaaf karne ke baad haaiza ho gaee thin, aap ne unhein bataya ke (unhein thaharney ki zarurat nahi balke) chali jaaein. lekin poochhney walon ne kaha ham aisa nahi karengey ke aap ki baat par amal to karein aur Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat chhod dein, Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke jab tum Madina pahunch jao to ye masla wahan (badey sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se) poochhna . chunanche jab ye log Madina aaey to poochha, jin akaabir se puchha gaya tha unmein Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) bhi thin aur unhon-ne (unke jawab mein wahi ( Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis bayan ki. us hadis ko Khalid aur Qatada ne bhi Ikrima se riwayat kya hai."
1759,"Madeena ke logon ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aik aurat ke mutaalliq puchha ke jo tawaaf karne ke baad haaiza ho gaee thin, aap ne unhein bataya ke (unhein thaharney ki zarurat nahi balke) chali jaaein. lekin poochhney walon ne kaha ham aisa nahi karengey ke aap ki baat par amal to karein aur Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat chhod dein, Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke jab tum Madina pahunch jao to ye masla wahan (badey sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se) poochhna . chunanche jab ye log Madina aaey to poochha, jin akaabir se puchha gaya tha unmein Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) bhi thin aur unhon-ne (unke jawab mein wahi ( Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis bayan ki. us hadis ko Khalid aur Qatada ne bhi Ikrima se riwayat kya hai."
1760,aurat ko uski ijazat hai ke agar wo tawaafe-ifaaza ( tawaaf ziyaarat ( kar chuki ho aur phir ( tawaaf wadaa' se pahley) haiz aa jaey to (apne ghar ( wapas chali jaey.
1761,us aurat ke liye waapsii nahi. iske baad maine unse suna aap farmatey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton ko uski ijazat di hai.
1762,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley, hamari niyat Haj ke siwa aur kuchh na thi. phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka) pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee ki, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram nahi khola kyonke aap ke sath qurbani thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon ne aur doosrey ashaab ne bhi tawaaf kya aur jinke sath qurbani nahi thin unhon-ne (is tawaaf w saee ke baad) ehram khol diya lekin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) haaiza ho gaee thin, sab ne apne Haj ke tamam manaasik ada kar liye they, phir jab lailatul-hasba yani rawaangii ki raat aai to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke tamam sathi Haj aur Umra donon karke ja rahe hain sirf mein Umra se mahroom hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha jab ham aaey they, to tum ( haiz ki wjah se) Baitullah ka tawaaf nahi kar saki thiin? maine kaha ke nahi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir apne bhai ke sath taneem chali ja aur wahan se Umre ka ehram baandh (aur Umra kar) ham tumhara falan jagah intizar karengey, chunanche main apne bhai (Abdur-Rehmaan (rz)) ke sath taneem gaee aur wahan se ehram baandhaa. isi tarah Safiya-bint-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) bhi haaiza ho gaee thin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein (az-raah muhabbat) farmaya ( عقرى حلقى ), Mina to, to hamein rok legii, kya tu ney qurbani ke din tawaafe-ziyaarat nahi kya tha? wo boliin ke kya tha, is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir koi harj nahi, chali chalo. mein jab aap tak pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka ke oopri ilaqe par chadh rahe they aur main utar rahi thi ya ye kaha ke main chadh rahi thi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) utar rahe they. Musaddad ki riwayat mein (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kehney par) haan ke bajaey nahi hai, uski mutabiat (pairavi) Jarir ne Mansoor ke waaste se ''nahin'' ke zikr mein ki hai."
1763,"mujhey wo hadis bataaey jo aapko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yad ho ke unhon-ne aathwein Zil-Hijja ke din Zohar ki Namaz kahan padhi thi, unhon-ne kaha Mina mein, maine puchha aur rawaangii ke din Asr kahan padhi thi unhon-ne farmaya ke Abtah main aur tum isi tarah karo jis tarah tumharey Hakim log kartey hun. (taake fitna waaqe na ho)."
1764,"Zuhar, Asr, maghrib, isha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne padhi aur thodi der ke liye Muhassab mein so rahe, phir Baitullah ki taraf Sawar ho kar gaey aur tawaaf kya. (yahaan tawaafe-ziyaara murad hai)."
1765,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Mina se kooch karke yahan Muhassab mein isliye utrey they taake aasani ke sath Madina ko nikal sakein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad Abtah mein utarney se thi.
1766,"Muhassab mein utarnaa Haj ki koi ibadat nahi hai, ye to sirf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qiyam ki jagah thi."
1767,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Makka jatey waqt zi tuwa ki donon pahaadiyon ke darmyan raat guzaartey they aur phir us pahaadii se ho kar guzartey jo Makka ke uper ki taraf hai aur jab Makka mein Haj ya Umre ka ehram baandhney aatey to apni ontni masjid ke darwaze par la kar bithatey phir hajre-Aswad ke paas aatey aur yahin se tawaaf shuru kartey, tawaaf saat (7) chakkaron mein khatm hota jiske shuru mein ramal kartey aur char mein mamool (routine) ke mutabiq chaltey, tawaaf ke baad 2 rakaat Namaz padhtey phir dera par wapas honey se pahley Safa aur Marwa ki daud kartey. jab Haj ya Umra karke Madina wapas hotey to zul-Hulaifa ke maidan mein sawari bithatey , jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi (Makka se Madina wapas hotey huey) apni sawari bithaya kartey they."
1768,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur umr aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muhassab mein qiyam farmaya tha. Naafe se riwayat hai ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Muhassab mein Zohar aur Asr padhtey they. mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne maghrib (padhney ka bhi) zikr kya, Khalid ne bayan kya ke isha mein mujhey koi shak nahi. iske padhney ka zikr zaroor kya phir thodi der ke liye wahan so rahtey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhi aisa hi mazkoor hai."
1769,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab Madina se Makka aatey to zii-Tuwa mein raat guzaarey aur jab subah sadiq hoti to Makka mein dakhil hotey . isi tarah Makka se waapsii mein bhi zii-Tuwa se guzartey aur wahin raat guzaarey aur farmatey ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi isi tarah kartey they.
1770,"zul-Majaaz aur Ukaaz ahade-jaahiliyat ke bazar they jab Islam aaya to maano logon ne (jaahiliyat ke un bazaron mein) khareed w farokht ko bura khayal kya. is par (sura al-Baqara ki) ye aayat nazil hui ''tumhaarey liye koi harj nahi agar tum apne rab ke Fazal ki talash karo, ye Haj ke zamane ke liye tha."
1771,"Makka se rawaangii ki raat Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) haaiza thin, unhon-ne kaha ke aisa malum hota hai main un logon ke rokney ka baais bin jaaungii , phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( عقرى حلقى ( kya tu ney qurbani ke din tawaafe-ziyaara kya tha? usne kaha ke ji haan kar liya tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir chalo."
1772,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (hijjatul-wadaa ( mein Madina se nikley to hamari zabanon par sirf Haj ka zikr tha. jab ham Makka pahunch gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ehram khol dene ka hukm diya ( Umra ada karney ke baad jinke sath qurbani nahi thi) rawaangii ki raat Safiya-bint-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) haaiza ho gain , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ( عقرى حلقى ( aisa malum hota ke tum hamein rokney ka baais banogii, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya qurbani ke din tum ne tawaafe-ziyaara kar liya tha? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir chali chalo! (Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne mutaalliq kaha ke) maine kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! maine ehram nahi khola hai aap ne farmaya ke tum taneem se Umre ka ehram baandh lo (aur Umra kar lo ( chunanche Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke sath unke bhai gaey ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) farmaya ke ham raat ke aakhir mein wapas lot rahe they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mulaqat hui, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke ham tumhara intizar falan jagah karengey."
